        "title": "Ibigori: Uburyo bwo kubihinga kijyambere n'ifumbire z'ikoreshwa",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "maize-plantation.jpg",
        "text": "<div class=\"post-thumbnail\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p><strong>Ibigori: Uburyo bwo kubihinga kijyambere n&rsquo;ifumbire z&rsquo;ikoreshwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikigori ni ikinyampeke gihingwa&nbsp; hafi ya hose mu Rwanda , mu butaka bufumbiye, burebure buhitisha amazi kandi bworoshye , haba i musozi cyangwa mu bishanga . Umurima uhingwamo ibigori ugomba kuba udaherukamo ibigori cyangwa ikindi kinyampeke nibura mu gihe cy&rsquo;igihembwe kimwe. Ibigori bikurikira ibinyamisongwe cyangwa ibinyabijumba</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gutegura umurima </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mbere yo guhinga ibigori, ni ngombwa kurwanya isuri mu murima icukura imirwanyasuri utera ibyatsi kuri iyo mirwanyasuri &nbsp;cyangwa ibiti bitangiza imyaka, cyangwa hagakorwa amaterasi y&rsquo;indinganire aho akenewe. Hakurikiraho kurima bwa mbere, gukuramo ibyatsi bidakenewe nk&rsquo;urwiri, no gutabira ugiye gutera imbuto.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Watera izihe mbuto, ku ruhe rugero?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ni byiza gukoresha imbuto z&rsquo;indobanure kugirango ubone umusaruro mwiza. Mu Rwanda, izo mbuto ziboneka mu kigo cy&rsquo;igihugu gishinzwe guteza imbere Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi(RAB), mu Makoperative no ku bikorera ku giti cyabo bafite uburenganzira bwo gutubura no gucuruza imbuto nziza. Amoko yamamazwa ni aya akurikira . Mu misozi migufi n&rsquo;iciriritse: Kigega(ZM 607), Pool 32. Mu misozi miremire hera Tamira(Pool 9), hari n&rsquo;imbuto bita &ldquo;Hybrid&rdquo; zihingwa igihembwe kimwe gusa , nka WH505, PAN 691, SC 525 na SC 513. Haterwa hagati y&rsquo;ibiro 20 na 25 z&rsquo;imbuto kuri Hegitari (Ha), ni ukuvuga intambwe ijana mu mpande zose.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ku murima muto wa Ari 10 , ni ukuvuga intambwe 100 ku ntambwe 10 , cyangwa se intambwe 50 kuri 20, haterwa hagati y&rsquo;ibiro 2 na 2.5 by&rsquo;imbuto. Ibigori biterwa ku mirongo itandukanyijwe na cm 70, naho hagati y&rsquo;ikigori n&rsquo;ikindi&nbsp; ugasigamo cm 30 hagaterwa intete 2 mu mwobo. Nyuma y&rsquo;ibyumweru bibiri uteye , ugenzura niba byose byarameze, ukagenda usimbura ibitarameze .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Igihe cyo gutera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibihe byo gutera biterwa n&rsquo;uturere : Mu misozi migufi batera mu minsi 15 ya mbere ya Nzeli cyangwa mu minsi 15 ya mbere ya Gashyantare . Mu gishanga batera muri: Nzeli na Werurwe, naho mu misozi miremire batera mu mezi y&rsquo;Ukuboza na Mata</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingano y&rsquo;ifumbire ikoreshwa </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu murima wa hegitari (Ha) ushyiramo toni 10 z&rsquo;ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera iboze neza mbere yo gutera . Uyinyanyagiza mu murima ugahita uyitaba , warangiza ugaca imirongo n&rsquo;imyobo uteramo. Wongeramo ibiro 100 bya DAP mu gihe cy&rsquo;itera. Uyora ifumbire mu gipfunsi ukagenda uyishyira ku buryo bumwe mu twobo. Utwobo tuba dufite ubujyakuzimu bwa cm 6.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ifumbire iri mu gipfunsi uyishyira mu twobo 6 kugeza ku 8 . Ushobora no gukoresha agafuniko ka byeri cyangwa fanta gacagase mu kobo kamwe . Iyo umaze gushyiramo ifumbire , uhita urenzaho agataka , maze ukabona&nbsp; gushyiramo&nbsp; imbuto, warangiza nay o ukayitwikiriza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nyuma y&rsquo;ibyumweru 6 cyangwa 7 uteye , ibigori bimaze kugira amababi byibura&nbsp; atatu, wongeramo ifumbire ya Uree ingana n&rsquo;ibiro 50 kg kuri Hegitari mu gihe&nbsp; cyo kubagara. Uca agaferege gato ku murongo ugororotse uteganye n&rsquo;uteyeho ibigori kuri cm 20 uvuye ku bigori , kugenda ushyiramo ifumbire ku buryo bumwe. Mu buryo bworoshye , ushobora gukoresha agafuniko k&rsquo;icupa rya byeri cyangwa Fanta . Iyo ako gafuniko kuzuye ifumbire ya Uree, uyitera mu ntera ya metero.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Mbere yo gutera ifumbire mu bigori , ndabanza nkabagara.</li>\r\no<li>Nkurikizaho guca agaferege gato ko guteramo ifumbire kuri cm 20 mvuye ku murongo w&rsquo;ibigori</li>\r\no<li>Ndatera ifumbire ku buryo bumwe</li>\r\no<li>Ifumbire nyirenzaho</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Indi mirimo y&rsquo;ingenzi ikorerwa ibigori </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uretse gufumbira , ni byiza&nbsp; kurwanya ibyatsi bibi mu murima , ubagara, umenera, usukira cyangwa ibyonnyi n&rsquo;indwara, kugira ngo bitagabanura umusaruro wari utegereje . Iyo ubonye nkongwa mu murima w&rsquo;ibigori, uyirwanya utera umuti wa Sumitiyo (Sumithion). Uvanga mililitio (ml) 10 mu mazi angina na litiro 10 ukawutera ahangana na m10 kuri m 10.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Wabona umusaruro ungana ute kandi ryari ?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibigori byerera iminsi 75 kugeza kuri 180 bitewe n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo;imbuto yahinzwe n&rsquo;akarere. Mu turere dushyuha, ibigori byera vuba kurusha udukonja . Umusaruro na wo uterwa n&rsquo;imbuto , ariko iyo wateye imbuto nziza kandi ugakurikiza amabwiriza ajyanye no guhinga ubona umusaruro wa toni 6 kuri hegitari.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Iyi mfashanyigisho tuyikesha Minisiteri y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;Ubworozi</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n",
