        "title": "Zimwe muri virusi zitera inyanya n'uburyo zivurwa",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "tomatospotted wilt virus2.jpg",
        "text": "<p>Indwara z&rsquo;inyanya ziterwa na Virusi ni nyinshi zitandukanye kandi zikanaterwa na Virusi zitandukanye. Gusa ibimenyetso byinshi byazo birasa kandi zose akaba ari indwara zidakira. Zikwirakwizwa n&rsquo;imbuto zo gutera,udusimba,ibikoresho n&rsquo;abahinzi.<br />\r\nZimwe muri virusi zifata inyanya tugiye kurebera hamwe uko zakwirindwa harimo Tomato mosaic virus,Tomato leaf curl virus bita imfunyarazi na Tomato spotted wilt virus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibimenyetso bigaragara ku nyanya zafashwe na Tomato mosaic Virus</strong><br />\r\nTomato mosaic virus,bita Mozayike ikwirakwizwa n&rsquo;inda ,ikagaragazwa n&rsquo;ibibara byerurutse ku mababi,bisa n&rsquo;umuhondo kandi amababi mato akarabirana. Igihingwa cyose kireruruka kandi ntikigire intege.<br />\r\nNaho Tomato Leaf curl virus,bita imfunyarazi ikwirakwizwa n&rsquo;isazi y&rsquo;umweru ,ikagaragazwa n&rsquo;amababi yikunja areba hejuru,amato akaza ariho ibibara by&rsquo;umuhondo nyuma nayo akikunja. Amababi akuze arakomera kandi ingingo z&rsquo;igihingwa zikaba ngufi.Igihingwa cyafashwe kireruruka kikagira udushami twinshi ku buryo gisa n&rsquo;igihuru.<br />\r\nVirusi yindi ni Tomato spotted wilt virus, ikwirakwizwa na Tiripusi,ikagaragazwa n&rsquo;ibibara ku mababi ,ku ruti no ku mbuto. Ku mababi mato hazaho ibibara by&rsquo;umukara by&rsquo;uruziga. Amababi ashobora kuba ikijuju nyuma akaba ikigina akuma.<br />\r\nKu mbuto kazaho amabara,zamara gushya,amabara akagaragara ari umuhondo uvanze n&rsquo;umutuku bikurikirana. Igihingwa kiraraba.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Izi Virusi zishobora kurwanywa</strong><br />\r\nMu kurwanya izi virusi,umuhinzi atera imbuto z&rsquo;indobanure. Arandura ibihingwa byagaragayeho uburwayi bwa virusi,ahinduranya ibihingwa mu murima,hirindwa gusimburanya inyanya n&rsquo;itabi,urusenda,puwavuro,intoryi,inzuzi n&rsquo;ibirayi.<br />\r\nUmuhinzi agerageza kurwanya udusimba twa Tiripusi,inda n&rsquo;isazi z&rsquo;umweru dukwirakwiza virusi,hakoreshwa imiti nka Dimethoate. Umuhinzi agomba gusukura ibikoresho mbere na nyuma yo kujya mu murima. Umuhinzi n&rsquo;undi wese bagomba kwirinda kugenda mu murima urimo uburwayi,nyuma bakajya mu murima muzima.<br />\r\nNi byiza ko umuhinzi abagara akanasasiza ibyatsi&nbsp; byumye</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n<p>Ngubwo bumwe mu buryo bwo kurwanya virusi zifata inyanya abahinzi bakoresha,nk&rsquo;uko tubikesha igitabo cya NAEB kivuga ku byonnyi no ku ndwara by&rsquo;imboga n&rsquo; imbuto. N&rsquo;ah&rsquo;abahinzi gukurikiza impanuro bahabwa</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Afoto amwe atwereka uko iyo ndwara ihindura urunyanya</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/tomatospotted-wilt-virus2.jpg\"><img alt=\"tomatospotted wilt virus2\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/tomatospotted-wilt-virus2.jpg?w=300&amp;h=157\" style=\"height:157px; width:300px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/tomato-mosaic-virus2.jpg\"><img alt=\"tomato mosaic virus2\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-7\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/tomato-mosaic-virus2.jpg?w=300&amp;h=135\" style=\"height:135px; width:300px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/tomatospotted-wilt-virus.jpg\"><img alt=\"tomatospotted wilt virus\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-8\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/tomatospotted-wilt-virus.jpg?w=300&amp;h=212\" style=\"height:212px; width:300px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/tomato-mosaic-virus.jpg\"><img alt=\"tomato mosaic virus\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-9\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/tomato-mosaic-virus.jpg?w=300&amp;h=212\" style=\"height:212px; width:300px\" /></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n",
