        "title": "Poivron: Tumenye uko ihingwa n'uburyo yitabwaho bya kijyambere ",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "poivronn.jpg",
        "text": "<p><strong>Uko ihingwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Poivron bayitera bahereye ku mbuto cyangwa umurama wayo hanyuma ukazigemura ku buryo hagati y&rsquo;urugemmwe n&rsquo;urundi hajyamo cm 30.<br />\r\nKuzigemura bikorwa nyuma y&rsquo;ibyumweru 4-5 bitewe n&rsquo;ahantu kandi zigahita ziterwa mu myobo.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n<p><strong>Gutegura umurima</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umurima ugomba guhingwa neza ugeza isuka mu butaka cyane ndetse ugakuramo ibinonko byose ubutaka bukaba bunoze.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kwita ku gihingwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ni ibikorwa bikubiyemo gutera umuti, kugerageza kubiterana n&rsquo;ibindi bihingwa kugirango bifashanye gukura , gusimburanya ibihingwa na poivron kugirango ubutaka bwisubize, Gusasira poivron, iyo igihingwa kimaze kuzana imbuto kiraremera hejuru niyo mpamvu bisaba gushyiraho uduti tubifata.<br />\r\nInyoni n&rsquo;ibindi byonyi biguruka bikunda kuba imbogamizi. Hari n&rsquo;igihe ubukonje buba bwinshi icyo gihe bisaba kuba warateye ibihingwa byawe ku buryo butandukanye kugiramgo umwanya wo guhumekeramo uboneke.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gusarura</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ni byiza gukoresha imikasi yabugenewe usarura kugirango udakurura urubuto ukangiza n&rsquo;ishami rufasheho ryose.<br />\r\nUmusaruro = 10 000 kg/ha<br />\r\nKwera biterwa n&rsquo;ubwoko wahinze , ariko muri rusange zerera iminsi 55-84 ku butumburuke hagati ya 0-2000m hejuru y&rsquo; inyanja. Ushobora kumenya ko imbuto zawe zeze urebeye ku ibara ryazo(umutuku cyangwa umuhondo bitewe n&rsquo;ubwoko wateye), ubunini cyangwa igihe zimaze mu murima. Gusarura bikorwa buri munsi kandi zigahita zijyanwa ku isoko. Zitwarwa neza kugirango hirindwe ko zangirika igihe zitwarwa ku&rsquo;isoko.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kuzicuruza</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zicuruzwa kw&rsquo;isoko, mu mahoteri mu ma restorant ako kanya zikiva mu murima. Igiciro kigenda gihinduka bitewe n&rsquo;igihe ndetse n&rsquo;uko ziri kuboneka kw&rsquo;isoko.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n",
