        "title": "Indwara z'inkwavu",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "inkwavu .png",
        "text": "<p><strong>Indwara z&rsquo;inkwavu</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu nkuru twabagejejeho ziheruka twabaganiriye ku bworozi bw&rsquo;inkwavu uburo bukorwa . Abakunzi bacu badusabye ko twabashakira ibijyanye n&rsquo;indwara z&rsquo;inkwavu dore ko bivugwako zikunda kurwaragurika akenshi zigapfira rimwe. Aha rero twifashishije imfashanyisgisho zateguwe na Minagri twabakusanyirije indwara zikunze kwibasira inkwavu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Niba ubonye ibimenyetso by&rsquo;indwara zimwe muri izi ihutire kureba umuntu ushinzwe kuvura amatungo mu gace utuyemo agufashe gusobanukirwa n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo;imiti ivugwa muri iyi nyandiko.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari indwara zitandukanye mu bworozi bw&rsquo;inkwavu, ariko izikunda kugaragara cyane ni izi zikurikira:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><strong>Impiswi: </strong>ni indwara ikunze kwibasira cyane inkwavu zicutse ziri hagati y&rsquo;ukwezi kumwe n&rsquo;amezi abiri. Iyo ndwara irazica cyane, niyo zibayeho zikura nabi cyane. Iyo ndwara itera igihombo mu bworozi bw&rsquo;inkwavu. Impiswi iterwa ahanini no gukangwa, guhindurirwa indyo,isuku nkeya n&rsquo;ibindi. Ibyo byose byiyongera cyane kubera agakoko gakunda kwibasira inkwavu cyane kitwa <em>coccidie</em>.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Impamvu zimwe mu zishobora gutiza umurindi indwara y&rsquo;impiswi ni: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Gukoranwa urugendo zikimara gucuka;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Guhindurirwa utuzu, ku bana bacutse;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Gusurwa n&rsquo;abashyitsi badasanzwe, cyangwa n&rsquo;inyamaswa;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Urusaku rudasanzwe inkwavu zitamenyereye;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Kubura ubwatsi bukomeye rimwe na rimwe (cyane mu gihe &ndash; cy&rsquo;itumba);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Guhindurirwa indyo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Impamvu nyazo zitera impiswi y&rsquo;inkwavu</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Ubwatsi bwanduye, indyo imunzwe</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Mikorobi na virusi zandura</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Mikorobi zisanzwe ziba mu mubiri nkeya zikorana nawo ariko zishobra kuhinduka umubiri kubera ko wacitse intege cyangwa wahinduriwe uburyo bwo kubaho.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-coccidie</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibimenyetso byayo </strong>: inkwavu zibanza kunanirwa kurisha, mu minsi itatu ya mbere, hanyuma zigahitwa, ariko iyo guhitwa ntikugaragara cyane, usibye kubona inyuma handuye kubera yo. Nyuma y&rsquo;iyo minsi, niho uko guhitwa kugaragara neza, inkwavu zigahekenya amenyo, zigapfa ku bwinshi, ariko izidapfuye zikira vuba.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imiti irwanya <em>coccidiose </em>akenshi ihagarika n&rsquo;ibindi bibazo by&rsquo;impiswi:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; <em>Sulfadimethoxine: </em>0; 5-07 g/l kuvura indwara;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>0,25 g/l kurwanya indwara;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; <em>Sulfaquinoxaline : </em>1g/l kuvura indwara;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>0,5g/l kurwanya indwara.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2.Inzoka zo mu nda </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ntabwo tuzitindaho cyane kuko na zo zikunze gutera ibibazo byo mu nda nk&rsquo;ibyo twavuze haruguru. Muri make turibanda ku buryo bwo kuzirwanya:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Kwirinda kwahira ubwatsi ahantu hakunze kugenda imbwa;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Kwirinda kwahira ubwatsi hari ikime;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Kwanika ubwatsi akanya gato mbere yo kubuha inkwavu;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Kumanika ubwatsi bugaburirwa inkwavu mu kazu kazo kugirango zitabwanduza</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Gukora isuku mu kazu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Gutanga imiti y&rsquo;inzoka</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imiti myiza ni <em>Ivermectin, Levamisole, Amprolium </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inkwavu zigomba guhabwa umuti wo kuzirinda inzoka buri mezi atatu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3.Indwara Zo Mu Myanya Y&rsquo;ubuhumekero </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibimenyetso by&rsquo;izo ndwara ni ibi bikurikira: urukwavu ruta ibimyira, ruritsamura buri kanya, rwishima ku zuru rukoresheje utuguru tw&rsquo;imbere</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Utwo ducurane twari utuzi nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi itatu duhinduka umuhondo. Hakurikiraho inkorora, hashobora kuziramo umusonga, impiswi, ibibazo by&rsquo;amaso, sinusite &sbquo;soma sinizite), umuhaha n&rsquo;ibindi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Impamvu ikunze gutera iyo ndwara : </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>-ubukonje</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-imikungugu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-umuyaga</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-micorobe</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-virusi</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uburyo bwo kuyivura: Hakunze gukoreshwa imiti nka: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>-Tetracycline </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>-Chloremph&eacute;nicore </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>-Sulfadimetoxine </em></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\no<li><strong>Uruheri rwo mu matwi no ku mubiri </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Udukoko twitwa <em>Psoroptes </em>cyangwa <em>Chorioptes </em>nitwo tuyitera. Hashobora kwivangamo na mikorobi, bikazana ibikoroto n&rsquo;umwanda byuzura mu gutwi ku buryo kuremerera urukwavu ikaguhengeka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Kuyivura, : Iyo ndwara ivurwa igitangira, naho ubundi irananirana: </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Imiti ikunze gukoreshwa ni</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ndash; Ivermectine </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ndash; malathion </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ndash; glyc&eacute;rine </em>cyangwa amavuta arimo iyode (<em>huile iod&eacute;e) </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;<em>Lindane </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Guhindura icyari kenshi</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\no<li><strong>Ibihushi </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyo ndwara ntiboneka kenshi ariko kuyivura biratinda kandi iteza ibihombo kuko imiti yayo irahenda. Umuti ukunzwe gukoreshwa ni <em>Gris&eacute;ofulvine. </em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa: </strong>ibivugwa muri iyi nkuru twabashakiye bigombwa gukurikizwa hakurikijwe nanone inama wahawe n&rsquo;ushinzwe ubwororozi mu gace uherereyemo.</p>\r\n",
