        "id": 163,
        "title": "Intama: Tumenye byinshi ku bworoziÂ bw'Intama n'uburyo bukorwa",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "intama.jpg",
        "text": "<p>Menya byinshi bitandukanye ku bworozi bw&rsquo;intama, ushobora kuba wibazaga uti ese intama iba mu kiraro kingana gute? Ese zororoka gute? Hamwe nibindi bibazo byose wibazaga kuri iri tungo nibyo tugiye kukugezaho mubushakashatsi twagukusanyirije .</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><strong>Uko ikiraro kigomba kuba kingana</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Inyagazi y&rsquo;intama iri kumwe n&rsquo;abana bayo kugeza bacutse ikenera ahantu hafite m<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">2</span></sup> 1.5</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Isekurume y&rsquo;intama ikenera m<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">2</span></sup> 2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Naho umwana w&rsquo;intama ufite umunsi n&rsquo;amezi 8 ugakenera m<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">2</span></sup> 0.7</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\no<li><strong>Kororoka</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>* Ku ntama 100 zimye, habyara 85</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Ku ntama 100 zibyara, havuka abana 140 ku nyarwanda na 180 ku za kijyambere</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Intama ibangurirwa bwa mbere imaze amezi 8 ivutse, icyo gihe iba ifite ibiro hafi 23 ku za kijyambere na 12 ku za kinyrwanda.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Isekurume imwe irahagije ku nyagazi 50, igatangira kwimya imaze amezi 15 ivutse.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Intama ihaka amezi 149-152 (amezi 5)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Yonsa buri mezi atatu, ishobora kubyara buri mezi 9 iyo yorowe kijyambere</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Intama iba ishaje iyo imaze imyaka 6-7 iba itangiye gukuka amenyo bahita bayikura mu bworozi.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\no<li><strong>Igaburo</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Intama itungwa n&rsquo;ibyatsi</li>\r\no<li>Ni byiza kuyongera igaburo iyo ihaka, bayiha imvange gr 100-150 ku munsi (mu mezi abiri yanyuma) bituma ibyara abana beza kandi bigatuma nayo ikomeza kuba nziza.</li>\r\no<li>Iyo yonsa bayiha 300-400 buri munsi bakurikije umubare w&rsquo;abana</li>\r\no<li>Isekurume bayiha gr 300 y&rsquo;imvange iyo yimya</li>\r\no<li>Iyo icutse bayiha gr 50-100 z&rsquo;imvange ku munsi.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\no<li><strong>Umusaruro</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Intama iyo ibazwe itanga inyama ku rugero rwa 48% kugeza kuri 50% kuzimeze neza</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\no<li><strong>Indwara z&rsquo;intama</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><strong>Inzoka zo munda: </strong>iyi ndwara ifata intama nkuru n&rsquo;intoya, igaragazwa no kudakura neza, guhitwa, kunanuka, no gukorora. Iyi ndwara irwanywa hakoreshejwe kugira isuku n&rsquo;imiti y&rsquo;inzoka igihe cyose iyi ndwara yagaragaye.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Ibinwanwa (Ibimwete): </strong>Iyi ndwara nayo ifata intama ntoya cyane cyane n&rsquo;inkuru , igaragazwa no kugira urukoko ku munwa, ibimwete mu kanywa bigakurikirwa no kubyimba amara bikazana n&rsquo;ingorane mu guhumeka.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Ibivuvumvuri byo mu gihanga: </strong>iyi ndwara ifata intama nkuru ikagaragazwa no kuzengera no kubyimba mu gihanga, irwanywa hakoreshejwe kurwanya isazi.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Ibisebe byo mu binono: </strong>Iyi ndwara ifata intama nkuru n&rsquo;intoya bimwe mu bimenyetso biyigaragaza; uruhu rwo hagati mu binono rureruruka bikanuka cyane, hakazamo ikibyimba urwara rukavaho, kuyirwanya ni ukoza neza mu binono na anticeptique, no gutera antibiotique.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
