        "id": 180,
        "title": "Soya: Uburyo bwo guhinga soya bya kijyambere",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "soya.jpg",
        "text": "<p>Mwireweho nshuti dusangiye kandi dusangira ubumenyi butandukanye ku buhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi ? Tugiye kurebera hamwe byinshi bitandukanye ku gihingwa cya Soya.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p><strong>ESE SOYA IHINGWA HE?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Soya ni igihingwa gikunda ubutaka bw&rsquo;isi ndende bufite ifumbire ihagije kandi butuma umwuka ubutemberamo. Amoko ya soya yamamazwa twavuga nka Bossier, Peka 6 na 449/6/16.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NI GUTE UMURIMA WO GUHINGAMO SOYA UTEGURWA?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari imirimo y&rsquo;ingenzi ikorwa mbere. harimo nko kurwanya isuri, kurima bwa mbere no kurima bwa kabiri ribyo gutabira bagiye gutera imbuto, hakaza igikorwa cyo gufumbira aho bashyiramo toni 10 z&rsquo;ifumbira y&rsquo;imborera iboze neza mu gihe cy&rsquo;itabira, bakongeramo ifumbire mvaruganda kg 100 za DAP mu gihe cy&rsquo;itera nyuma bagashyiramo rizobiyumu (mikorobi) mu mbuto mbere yo gutera hakoreshwejwe agapfunyika ka g 40 kavangwa n&rsquo;ibiro 2 by&rsquo;imbuto. Hakaza gutera imbuto: umuhinzi akoresha kg 70 kuri Ha, agatera kuri cm 40 hagati y&rsquo;imirongo na cm 10 ku mirongo ashyira intete imwe mu kobo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NB: </strong>Igihe cyiza cy&rsquo;itera ni muri nzeri no muntangiriro ya Gashyantare bitewe n&rsquo;igihe igihembwe cy&rsquo;ihinga cyatangiriye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/04/soja.jpg\"><img alt=\"soja\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-87\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/04/soja.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GUFATA NEZA SOYA MU MURIMA: </strong>Mu mirimo y&rsquo;ingenzi twavuga kubagara no gusukira soya ifite amababi ane. Umuhinzi kandi agomba kurwanya indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi hakoreshwejwe amoko yihanganira indwara, baterera igihe ndetse n&rsquo;imiti.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IBYONNYI N&rsquo;INDWRA BYANGIZA SOYA</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><strong>IBYONNYI: 1. Inyoni:</strong> iyo imvura iguye mu murima ukimara guterwamo soya izsanza umurima maze soya ikajya hejuru icyo gihe inyoni, inkoko cangwa inuma zira ya soya niyo mpamvu soya igomba giterwa mu bujya kuzimu buhagije kandi ugashyira abana abana mu murima kugeza igihe soya izamukiye yose mu butaka, soya kandi yongera kurindwa iyo itanhiye kwera kugeza ishize mu murima.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Nyamwihina: </strong>Ni agakoko ko mubwoko bw&rsquo;ibinyugunyugu kitwa lamprosema indicate, igihingwa cyafashwe naka gakoko usanga imamabi azingiye hamwe nk&rsquo;azirikishijwe urudodo nyamwihina irimo imbere. Yonera munsi y&rsquo;ikibabi itagipfumuye kandi igaragara igihe soya itangiye kurabya kandi hari izuba. Aka gakoko bakarwanya bakoresheje umuti witwa cypermethrine cyangwa deltamethrine cyangwa fenvalerate.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>B.INDWARA: </strong>Indwara y&rsquo;utudomo tw&rsquo;amababi iterwa n&rsquo;agahumyo bita Pyrenochaeta glycines, igaragazwa nuko amababi azaho utudomo tujya kuba uruziga tw&rsquo;ikigina kijya gusa n&rsquo;ibihogo, iyo amaze igihe kirekire agenda aba ikijuju azengurutswe n&rsquo;ikigina kijimye kijya kuba umukara, iyi ndwara yibasira cyane ibibabi byo basi ikagaragara cyane mu gihe cy&rsquo;imvura. Uburyo iyi ndwara irwanywamo ni ugusimburanya imyaka soya ikazamo hashize imyaka ibiri.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IGIHE YERERA: </strong>Soya yerera iminsi 100 cyangwa 130 bitewe nubwoko bwayo, kuri Ha hera hagati ya toni 1,2 na toni 1,6.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n",
