        "title": "Urutoki: Guhinga urutoki bya kijyambere",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "urutokii.jpg",
        "text": "<p>Ruhingwa cyane ku nkombe z&rsquo;i Kivu, umurambi n&rsquo;umukenke by&rsquo;iburasirazuba. Ruhingwa mu butaka bw&rsquo;ibumba rivanze n&rsquo;imborera kandi buhitisha amazi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amoko yamamazwa:</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Ibitoki biribwa: Ingaju, Mbwaziruma, Injagi, Mpologoma,<br />\r\nIcyerwa,&hellip;<br />\r\n&bull; Ibitoki by&rsquo;imineke: Poyo, Kamaramasenge, FHIA 17, FHIA 25, Gros<br />\r\nMichel, &hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gutegura umurima:</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Kurwanya isuri.<br />\r\n&bull; Guhinga umurima.<br />\r\n&bull; Gucukura imyobo ya cm 60 z&rsquo;ubujyakuzimu na cm 60<br />\r\nz&rsquo;umurambararo; ubutaka buvuye hejuru busubizwa mu mwobo bukavangwa n&rsquo;ifumbire.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gufumbira:</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Bashyira Kg 20 z&rsquo;ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera iboze neza mu mwobo umwe.<br />\r\n&bull; Bakongeramo g 125 za NPK17.17.17 cyangwa g 125 za Urea, mu mwobo, mu gihe cy&rsquo;itera .<br />\r\n&bull; Nyuma insina zimaze gukura, ifumbire ijya ishyirwa ku muzenguruko w&rsquo;insina (muri cm 60) mu ibimba ritari rirerire kugira ngo imizi y&rsquo;insina itangirika (rimwe cyangwa kabiri mu mwaka).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gutera imibyare:</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Batera imibyare ivuye mu rutoki rutarwaye kandi rwera neza, isongoye hejuru, ifite inguri nini, imizi n&rsquo;ibitaka byavanweho; ikagira n&rsquo;uburebure buri hagati ya cm 80 na m 1,50.<br />\r\nBatera imibyare iri hagati ya 1.100 kuri Ha.<br />\r\n&bull; Batera kuri m 3 hagati y&rsquo;imirongo na m 3 ku mirongo (hagati y&rsquo;umwobo n&rsquo;undi), bitewe n&rsquo;ubwoko.<br />\r\n&bull; Bashyira umubyare umwe mu mwobo.<br />\r\n&bull; Igihe cy&rsquo;itera: biba byiza cyane iyo urutoki rutewe mu mvura y&rsquo;umuhindo yo muri Nzeri cg Ukwakira kuko imvura y&rsquo;impeshyi isanga zimaze gukura. Icyakora no mu mvura ya Gashyantare bashobora gutera urutoki.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kurukenura (Kurukorera cg Kurufata neza):</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Gusasira, gushangurura, kuzicira, gukata imyanana, kuzitega inzego.<br />\r\n&bull; Kurimbura inguri zishaje.<br />\r\n&bull; Gusimbura urutoki rushaje.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Igihe rwerera:</strong><br />\r\n&bull; Hagati y&rsquo;amezi 12 na 15 ku bitoki by&rsquo;inzoga n&rsquo;ibiribwa.<br />\r\n&bull; Hagati y&rsquo;amezi 18 na 20 ku bitoki by&rsquo;imineke.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi</strong><br />\r\nIndwara z&rsquo;ingenzi n&rsquo;uburyo zirwanywa</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Indwara ya Fizariyoze iterwa n&rsquo;agahumyo bita Fusarium oxysporium f. sp. cubense; insina yafashwe amakoma agenda ahinduka umuhondo uhereye kuyo hasi. Nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi mike amakoma aruma maze agatendera ku mutumba, umwumba nawo uhita wuma. Iyo utemye umutumba usangamo ububore bugaragazwa n&rsquo;amabara y&rsquo;ikigina n&rsquo;ayirabura. Iyi ndwara yibasira cyane ubwoko bw&rsquo;insina za Kayinja, Gros michel, Kamaramasenge n&rsquo;izindi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Basarura hagati ya 8 T na 35 T/Ha z&rsquo;ibitoki bitewe n&rsquo;ikoranabuhanga.<br />\r\n&bull; Babica igihe bikomeye, bagahita babiteka cyangwa babitara hanyuma bakabivanamoumutobe, urwagwa&hellip;.; mu nganda bavanamo ibisuguti na za divayi zinyuranye.</p>\r\n",
