        "id": 183,
        "title": "Uburyo bwo guhinga Inkeri bwa kijyambere ",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "inkeri2.jpg",
        "text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:null\">Izina nyabuhanga: Fragaria</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Ubwoko bw&rdquo;igihingwa: Imbuto</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Izuba gihenera: Ryinshi</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Ubutaka: Uruyungu</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Ubusharire bw&rsquo;ubutaka: pH 5.5-7(Slightly Acidic to Neutral)</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Inkeri ni igihingwa gifite uruti rworoshye n&rsquo;ibibabi birambuye by&rsquo;icyatsi kibisi, kikagira n&rsquo;indabo z&rsquo;umweru cyangwa z&rsquo;umuhondo, imbuto zacyo ni umutuku kandi zirahumura hamwe n&rsquo;ibibabi byawo, byose birakoreshwa.Inkeri zigiraumutobe mwinshi. Ni imbuto zoroshye kuzihinga iyo ufite ubushake .</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Uko zihingwa</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Inkeri ni igihingwa kirandaranda kandi uruti rwacyo rugenda rugaba amashami hose .</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Tegura umwobo uhagije uzabasha kwakira imizi yose y&rdquo;icyo gihingwa dore ko aba ari myinshi ariko ntucukure cyane .</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Tegura umwanya uhagije kugirango zizabone aho zirandaranda. Siga cm 50 hagati y&rsquo;ingemwe n&rsquo;indi na cm 120 hagati y&rsquo;imirongo ibiri.</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Ubusharire bw&rsquo;ubutaka bugomba kuba ari 5.5-7 , bibaye byiza wabitegura kare ushyiramo ibituma ubu busharire bungana gutya( amendment).</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Inkeri zikenera byibura amasaha 6-10 ku munsi zifite imirasire y&rsquo;izuba , tegura rero ahantu habereye iyo mirasire.</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Zikunda ubutaka bw&rsquo;uruyungu ariko n&rsquo;ahandi zahaba.</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Zihingwa ahantu humutse .</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Ntuzazitere ahantu hamaze kuva izindi nkeri , inyanya cyangwa urusenda.</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Byaba byiza buri ugiye usazura inkeri zawe kugirango zitange umusaruro wifuza.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Uko zitabwaho</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Ni byiza gukuraho uruyange rwazo ku nshuro ya mbere kugirango uzibuze gushyira ingufu nyinshi mu kurema imbuto ahubwo izo mbaraga zizishyire mu kwita ku mizi ihagije kugira ngo ku kuraba gukurikiyeho uzabone umusaruro mwinshi.</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Ubuhehere bw&rsquo;ubutaka ni ngombwa cyane dore ko n&rsquo;imizi iba itari kure cyane , zikenera amazi menshi iyo ziri kuraba ndetse no mu gihe zifite imbuto</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Ugomba kuzisasira kugirango ubuhehere bw&rsquo;ubutaka bwiyongere.</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Kuraho ibyatsi by&rsquo;ibyonnyi byose kuko bitwara intunga gihingwa nyinshi cyane cyane mu kwezi kwa mbere umaze kuzitera kandi ubikoreshe intoki.</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Ubishoboye watwikira neza uruyange kuko inyoni zirarukunda .</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Gusarurwa</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Imbuto zisarurwa nyuma y&rsquo;ibyumeru 4-6 nyuma yo kuzana uruyange</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Sarura gusa imbuto zahishije</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Sarurana urubuto n&rsquo;agati karuhuza n&rsquo;igihingwa kugirango rutangirika</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Ushobora kuzishyira muri Frigo umaze kuzisarura iminsi 3-5</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Zishobora kumara amezi abiri muri frigo bitewe n&rsquo;ubwoko wahinze</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Mu bindi</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Igihugu cya mbere mu guhinga Inkeri kw&rsquo;isi ni Leta zunze ubumwe za America naho muri Afurika ni Misiri</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Inkeri ni imbuto zishimishije, zikoreshwa mu kurwanya udukoko twose two ku mubiri kandi zituma umuntu akura neza,zikomeza amagufa kandi zifasha n&rsquo;abantu bagaragayeho kutarya neza. Inkeri kandi zirimo imyunyu ngugu ikenerwa cyane n&rsquo;abantu barwaye za gute (goutte) bababara no mu mubiri.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Nutritional value per 100 g (3.5 oz)</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Energy</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">136 kJ (33 kcal) </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Carbohydrates 7.68 g</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Sugars 4.89 g</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Dietary fiber 2 g</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Fat 0.3 g</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Protein 0.67 g</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:'Helvetica','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"color:#141823\"><span style=\"background-color:null\">Amazi 90.95 g</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"background-color:null\">Fluoride 4.4 &micro;g</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n",
