        "id": 184,
        "title": "Uko makadamiya (macadamia) ihingwa, aho yera n'uburyo yitabwaho",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "macadamia-01.jpg",
        "text": "<p><strong>Aho macadamia yera mu Rwanda:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p>Makadamiya ishobora kwera ahantu hose hera Kawa hafite imvura ya mm 800-1900 n&rsquo;ubutumburuke bw&rsquo;imisozi migufi kugera ku miremire ya metero 750-2.250. Yihanganira imvura nke kurusha Kawa, iri hagati ya mm 750-1.000 nkuko byagaragaye i Karama mu Bugesera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uturere tuberanye na macadamia:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>(a) Utuberanye na Macadamia cyane: Umurambi wo hagati mu Rwanda n&rsquo;uturere tw&rsquo;urusekabuye(Intara y&rsquo;amajyepfo n&rsquo;iyiburasira zuba,n&rsquo;amajyepfo y&rsquo;intara y&rsquo;amajyaruguru),umurambi w&rsquo;iburasizuba n&rsquo;nkengero z&rsquo;ikiyaga cya Kivu n&rsquo;Impala.<br />\r\n(b) Uturere tuberanye na Macadamia mu rugero: Bugesera, Mayaga, Umukenke w&rsquo;iburasirazuba, Isunzu rya Kongo-Nil ryose.<br />\r\n(c) Uturere tuberanye na Macadamia buhoro: Akarere k&rsquo;amakoro, imisozi miremire y&rsquo;ububeruka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amoko :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Makadamia ifite amoko abiri, hari ubwoko bufite igishishwa cyoroshye n&rsquo;amavuta menshi(73-78% ariyo Macadamia Integrifolia) ari nayo yamamazwa mu Rwanda, muri Africa no ku isi yose n&rsquo;ubwoko bufite igishishwa gikomeye n&rsquo;amavuta make (Macadamia Tetraphylia)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingengabihe no gutunganya imbuto n&rsquo;ingemwe:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Igiti cya Macadamia kirakura kikageza ku burebure bwa metero 10- 15.Gisaba ubushyuhe bwa 15-28&deg;c. Imbuto z&rsquo;indobanure zikwiranye n&rsquo;uturere nizo batera,ingero ni nka KRG15,EMB-1,MRG-20 na KMB z&rsquo;ikigo cy&rsquo;ubushakashatsi mu buhinzi cya Kenya(KARI) zamamazwamu Rwanda.<br />\r\nImbuto zinikwa mu mazi amasaha 72 (iminsi 3), bahindura amazi buri munsi kugira ngo zidahuguta, ziterwa mu buhumbikiro bufite imitabo ya metero 1 y&rsquo;ubugari na metro 8-10 z&rsquo;uburebure irimo umusenyi wa centimetro 20 z&rsquo;ubujyakuzimu. Batera mu mirongo ya centimetero 8 hagati y&rsquo;umurongo n&rsquo;undi, centimetero 1 hagati y&rsquo;urubuto n&rsquo;urundi na centimetero 3 z&rsquo;ibujyakuzimu. Zimera nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 21-45, ni ngombwa kuzivomera buri munsi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nyuma y&rsquo;amezi abiri bazigemurira mu bihoho bya cm 15 z&rsquo;umurambararo kuri cm 18 z&rsquo;uburebure, z&rsquo;ifite ibibabi 4 bikomeye.<br />\r\nBazishyira muri pepiniyeri isakaye ku buryo itanga urumuri rwa 40- 50% zikamaramo amezi 2 kugeza kuri 3. Ingemwe bazibangurira zimaze amezi 6 kugera kuri 12 bazigemuye ziba zifite uburebure bwa cm 10-15 zifite ibibabi 8 cg 10.Nyuma yo kubangurira zimurirwa muri pepiniyeri aho zimara amezi 2-3 aho zibona urumuri rungana na 40-50%. Mbere yo kuzitera mu murima zimenyerezwa izuba andi mezi 2-3.Ingemwe ziterwa mu murima ziteguwe amazi 18.<br />\r\nMu gushyira igitaka mu bihoho, ntibuzuza umwobo kugirango haboneke ahazashyirwa amazi avomerera, bavomerera 3 mu cyumweru mu mezi 3 ya mbere<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><strong>Uko Batera Makadamia N&rsquo;imirimo Ikorerwa Ingemwe Ziterwa.</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umurima utunganywa neza mu gihe cy&rsquo;izuba(icyi) barima inshuro 2 mbere yo gutera. Bacukura imyobo ya cm 60 z&rsquo;umurambararo na cm 60 z&rsquo;ibujyakuzimu bashyiramo udutebo 2 tw&rsquo;ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera ivanze n&rsquo;igitaka cyo hejuru na garama 60 za NPK 20.10.10.<br />\r\nBatera makadamia mu gihe cy&rsquo;imvura kuri metero 7.5 hagati y&rsquo;imirongo na metero 7.5 hagati y&rsquo;igiti n&rsquo;ikindi(ibiti 178 kuri ha) mu murima wihariye cg metero 10 na matero 10 hagati y&rsquo;imirongo n&rsquo;igiti n&rsquo;ikindi mu murima bazavanga n&rsquo;ibindi bihingwa. Kuvanga makadamiya n&rsquo;ibindi bihingwa bituma umurima ubyazwa umusaruro mwinshi mu gihe kimwe. Ibinyamisogwe nk`ibishyimbo, soya n`ubunyobwa byongera azote mu butaka. Ubwatsi bw&rsquo;amatungo nka desimodiyumu na Leuceana birwanya ibyatsi bibi. Imbuto ziribwa nka Maracuja, inanasi, amapapayi bibangikana neza na makadamiya.<br />\r\nBatera imirongo 2 cg 3 y&rsquo;imbuto ziribwa nyuma y&rsquo;umurongo 1 wa makadamiya, ni byiza kuyibangikanya n&rsquo;indi myaka mu myaka 7 ya mbere, bayitera no mpande z&rsquo;imirima no ku miryanyasuri.<br />\r\nBashingirira ingemwe kugirango zitazunguzwa n&rsquo;umuyaga mwinshi,basasira muri cm 10-15 uvuye ku giti, ntikunda gukatwa cyane.<br />\r\nBakuraho amashami yavunitse cg ayumye agakatwa yegerejwe igihimba kugirango igiti gihagarare neza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Isarura, umurumbuko n&rsquo;ikoreshwa rya makadamiya.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Igiti cya makadamiya kibanguriye gitangira kwera nyuma y&rsquo;imyaka 4-5. Umusaruro ugenda wiyongera uko kigenda gikura, igiti kimwe gitanga umurumbuko wa kilo 50-75 buri mwaka gifite imyaka 10-15.<br />\r\nKiraramba cyane kandi cyera neza kugeza ku myaka 80-100. Imbuto za makadamiya zeze zirigusha, zigatoragurwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 1-2.<br />\r\nNtibyemewe gusarura imbuto zikiri ku giti kuko utamenya izeze n&rsquo;iziteze. Zanikwa ku kidasesa gitobaguye gifite imyobo ya mm 6-7 ahantu hari igicucu kugirango zidaturagurika hakinjiramo udukoko twazangiza. Zihunikwa ahantu humutse kandi hari ubukonje n&rsquo;ubushyuhe buringaniye, kure y&rsquo;ibintu binuka byazitera nazo<br />\r\nkunuka, hatagera udukoko.<br />\r\nZiribwa zumye cg zikaranze. Mu nganda bakoramo ibisuguti, gato cyangwa se shokora, umushongi uryohera witwa &bdquo;ice cream&ldquo; n&rsquo;ibindi. Zikungahaye ku mavuta meza atekwa,mu nganda z&rsquo;imiti akorwamo amavuta yo kwisiga,ibikatsi bikorwamo ibribwa by&rsquo;amatungo,ibishishwa barabicana.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Intungamubiri, agaciro n&rsquo;inyungu makadamiya yazanira </strong><strong><strong>abahinzi bayo.</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imbuto za makadamiya zitanga ibivumbikisho bihanitse (Kcal 7.350 ku kilo), zifite amavuta menshi aruta ibindi bihingwa (73-78%) by&rsquo;ibinyamavuta (ubunyobwa 44.8%,soya-15.7%), kandi ntifite ibinure bitera indwara. Zikize muri vitamini( A, B,C) n&rsquo;imyunyu (Ca,P,Fer) Makadamiya irakenewe cyane ku isoko mpuzamahanga aho igura amadolari 10-20 ku Kilo. Umusaruro uboneka ku isi ni 45% ku ukenewe. Umuhinzi mu Rwanda yejeje kilo 50-75 ku giti kimwe igiciro ari 350 Rwf/kilo yabona amafaranga 17.500-26.000 ku giti 1 ku mwaka.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n",
