        "id": 187,
        "title": "Tumenye guhinga ingano ku buryo bwa kijyambere",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "ingano.png",
        "text": "<p>Ingano ni igihingwa gikunda ubutaka bw&rsquo;isi ndende bufite ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera ihagije kandi buhitisha amazi. Ni igihingwa kandi gikunda guhingwa mu turere tw&rsquo;amakoro no mu karere k&rsquo;isunzu rya Kongo nil. Ingano kandi igira amoko menshi arimo Musama, Bisagi na Uganda 6.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p><strong>Uko bategura umurima wo guhingamo Ingano</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu mirimo yingenzi twavuga kurwanya isuri, kurima bwa mbere no kurima bwa kabiri aribyo gutabira bagiye gutera imbuto.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko bafumbumbira umurima ugiye guterwamo Ingano </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bakoresha toni 10 z&rsquo;ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera iboze neza mbere yo kubiba. Bakongeramo ifumbire mvaruganda kg 250 za NPK 17 17 17 kuri Ha cyangwa kg 100 za DAP. Iyo fumbire ivangwa n&rsquo;imbuto mbere yo gutera. Nyuma y&rsquo;ibyumweru 6 bongeramo kg 100 za urea kuri Ha. Mu butaka busharira babanza gushyiramo toni 3,5 z&rsquo;ishwagara kuri Ha ikamaramo ibihe by&rsquo;ihinga bine(4 Seasons).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ingano y&rsquo;imbuto z&rsquo;Ingano iterwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umuhinzi akoresha kg 200 z&rsquo;imbuto z&rsquo;ingano kuri Ha. Atera kuri cm 20 hagati y&rsquo;imirongo kanda agatera hagati muri Nzeri no hagati ya Werurwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko bafata neza ingano mu murima</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu mirimo y;ingenzi twavuga nko kubagara no gusukira buhoro no kurwanya indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi hakoreshejwe amoko yihanganira indwara n&rsquo;imiti.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi byangiza Ingano</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><strong>Ibyonnyi: 1. Agakoko karya amababi: </strong>ni agakoko ko mu bwoko bw&rsquo;ibivumvuri bita <strong><em>Epilashna spp</em></strong>. Kameze nk&rsquo;impeke y&rsquo;ikawa. Ako gakoko gafite ibara ry&rsquo;umutuku ririmo utudomo twinshi tw&rsquo;umukara. Bakayirwanya bakoresheje imiti ya kizungu nka Dimethoate, Chrolopyrophos-ethyl na Cypermenthrine.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Indwara: 1. Seputoriyoze:</strong> Iterwa n&rsquo;agahumo bita <strong><em>Septoria tritici</em>.</strong> Iyi ndwara igaragazwa n&rsquo;amabara maremare atareshya y&rsquo;ikigina yeruruka mu ibara hagati, umuzenguruko w&rsquo;ibara ukaba ikigina kijimye. Iyi ndwara itangirira ku mababi hasi kandi iyo ibonete mu murima utarera ntacyo basarura. Ubusanzwe igabanya umusaruro w&rsquo;ingano kandi ikagaragara mu gihe guhehereye kirangwa n&rsquo;ubushyuhe. Bayirwanya batera imbuto ziyihanganira kandi zindobanure, guhingira igihe, guhungira imbuto mbera yo kuzitera.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Umugese w&rsquo;Ingano: </strong>Utwerwa nagahumyo bita <strong><em>Puccinia sp</em></strong> (striifomis, gramminis na recondida) iyi ndwara igaragazwa n&rsquo;udufumagure tw&rsquo;ifu tw&rsquo;umuhondo wijimye cyangwa tw&rsquo;umukara ku mababi y&rsquo;Ingano. Amababi yafashwe aruma ikunda kuboneka cyane mu gihe hakonje, kandi Ingano ziyirwaye zigira ibihuhwe byinshi. Iboneka cyane nyuma y&rsquo;itera. Bayirwanya batera imbuto ziyihanganira kare kandi zihungije umuti wa Thiram ndetse no gusimburanya ibihingwa mu murima kuko agahumyo kayitera gashobora kuba gafashe ku bishibu cyangwa ku ngemwe z&rsquo;Ingano z&rsquo;intete zaguye hasi.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Umusaruro w&rsquo;Ingano</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ushobora kwibaza uti Ingano yera mu gihe kingana gute? Ingano yera hagati y&rsquo;iminsi 120 cyangwa 140 bitewe n&rsquo;ubwoko bwayo, Umusaruro uboneka ni 3-4/Ha Ingano kandi zigomba gusarurwa zeze neza zigahunikwa ahantu humutse kandi hari umwuka uhagije.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Byateguwe na Jean Luc Mugiraneza hifashishijwe imfashanyigisho za MINAGRI</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n",
