        "id": 188,
        "title": "Uburyo bwo guhinga imyumbati kijyambere ",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "imyumbati.jpg",
        "text": "<p><strong>Aho imumbati ihingwa kandi yera neza:</strong> Itanga umusaruro mwiza mu Mayaga no mu Mirambi no mu mukenke by&rsquo;Iburirazuba.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><strong>Ubutaka :</strong> ni igihingwa gikunda ubutaka buseseka</li>\r\no<li><strong>Amoko yamamazwa:</strong> Hari amoko menshi ariko atangwa n&rsquo;ubishakashatsi ni aya:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><strong>Mu Miribwa:</strong> Ndamirabana(TME14). Mbakungahaze(95/NA/00063), Cyizere(192/0057),Mbagarumbise.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Mu bwoko bwa Gitaminsi:</strong> Creolina na Gakiza</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\no<li><strong>Gutegura umurima:</strong> Imirimo isabwa ni ibiri: Kurwanya isuri no gutegura umurima .</li>\r\no<li><strong>Gufumbira:</strong> bashyira toni 10-20 z&rsquo;ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera iboze neza bakongeramo kg 300/Ha za NPK 17.17.17 mu kaziga kazengurutse ingeri zimaze gufata.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Igera imbuto:</strong> Haterwa ingeri 10 000 kuri Ha 1 zavuye mu murima w&rsquo;imyumbati yera neza. Batera ingeri kuri m1 hagati y&rsquo;imirongo no kuri m1 hagati y&rsquo;ingeri n&rsquo;iyindi kandi hagashyirwa ingeri imwe mu mwobo. <strong>Igihe cyiza cy&rsquo;itera :</strong> ni hagati y&rsquo;Ukwakira n&rsquo;Ugushyingo</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\no<li><strong>Gufata neza imyumbati mu murima :</strong> Nyuma y&rsquo;ukwezi bamaze gutera imyumbati igomba kubagarwa, bakayisukira imaze kugira cm 60 z&rsquo;uburebure. Bongera kubagara iyo bibaye ngombwa imyumbati ifite amezi atatu.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Imbyonyi n&rsquo;indwara:</strong> mu kurwanya ibyonnyi n&rsquo;indwara, umuhinzi agomba gukoresha ubwoko bwihanganira indwara, guterera igihe akabona gukoresha ifumbire mvaruganda .</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><strong>Agatagangurirwa :</strong> ni agakoko gafite ibara ry&rsquo;icyatsi kibisi bita Mononychellus tanaioa twangiza imyumbati mu gihe cy&rsquo;izuba. Ku myumbati tugaragara ku mababi yo hejuru akivuka no ku mutwe w&rsquo;amashami kuko horoshye .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ikimenyetso:</strong> amababa usanga ari icyatsi kibisi kivanzemo utubara tw&rsquo; umuhondo kandi twinshi. Amababi ata ireme akagwingira ntakure . Ku mutwe w&rsquo;amashami hasigara utubabi tumeze nk&rsquo;utwana tw&rsquo;inyoni .Umwumbati ugira ingingo ngufi cyane .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko barwanya iyo ndwara:</strong> Gutera imyumbati yera vuba mu gihe imvura itangiye kugwa no gutera imyaka yihanganira agataganurirwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li><strong>Indwara y&rsquo;Ububembe:</strong> Ni indwara iterwa n&rsquo;agakoko ka virusi yitwa Cassava Mosaic Virus(CMV), iyo virus ikwirakwizwa n&rsquo;isazi yitwa Bemisia tabaci .Iyo ndwara ikunze kuboneka hose mu Rwanda.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibimenyetso:</strong> Indwara itangira ibibabi Bizana amabara y&rsquo;umuhondo, ahasigaye ari icyatsi hagakomeza gukura ugasanga ikibabi kiri kw&rsquo;ikunja kunja kigapfunyarara nyuma kikagira amatwi. Iyo bikabije umwumbati ukura nabi ukagwingira.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko bayirwanya:</strong> Umuhinzi ategekwa kurandura buri giti kirwaye mu murima , guhingira igihe, gutera imbuto nzima kandi z&rsquo;indobanure kandi zihanganira iyo ndwara.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu murima hagomba kandi kugirara isuku Imyumbati, no guhinga neza kandi agakumira ingaruka ziterwa na ya sazi.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"9\">\r\no<li><strong>Igihe yerera :</strong> imyumbati yera hagati y&rsquo;ameze 18-24 kuri gitaminsi. Naho ku myumbati y&rsquo;imiribwa ni hagati y&rsquo;amezi 10-15.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Gusarura no guhunika: </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Umusaruro ukunze kuboneka uri hagati ya toni 20 na toni 20 z&rsquo;imyumbati kuri Ha.</li>\r\no<li>Naho ku birebana n&rsquo;ihunika imyumbati iguma mu murima ikazakurwa bibaye ngombwa cyangwa ikabikwa ahantu humutse ari imivunde yumye.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n",
