        "title": "Uko wakora ifumbire isukika iwawe mu rugo",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "gukora ifumbire isukikag.jpg",
        "text": "<p><strong>Ikorere ifumbire isukika mu rugo iwawe wongere umusaruro</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p>Ubu butaka bwaba bwera? Abantu benshi bibaza iki kibazo iyo bagiye kugura ubutaka bazakoreramo ibikorwa by&rsquo;ubuhinzi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iki kibazo gishobora gusubizwa neza hakozwe ipimwa ry&rsquo;ubutaka, ariko buri muhinzi byibura agomba kumenya ibyingenzi mu bwiza bw&rsquo;ubutaka n&rsquo;uburyo bwo guhinga neza hitabwa kuri ubu bwiza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu butaka, tureba inkomoko y&rsquo;ubwiza bw&rsquo;ubutaka duhereye ku bintu bibibi: Mbere na mbereduhera ku Rutare ubutaka bukomokaho .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urwo rutare rutanga intungagihingwa binyuze bu buryo rugenda ruvaho uduce turugize (weathering), twavuga nk&rsquo;uburyo bwo kubonamo twa turema butaka duto duto tumeze nk&rsquo;umukungugu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nanone ubwiza bw&rsquo;ubutaka tububona duhereye ku gice kigaragara hejuru kigize ubutaka kigizwe n&rsquo;ibintu byose bimera cyangwa bitwikiriye isi birimo ibibora.Ibi byose rero nibyo bigenda bigahura n&rsquo;udusimba duto tuba mu butaka hanyuma utwo dusimba tugafasha mu kubihindura imborera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyi mborera kongeraho twa duce tumeze nk&rsquo;umukungugu twaturutse ku rutare rugize isi bitaga utubumbe umuntu ashobra kubonesha amaso (aggregates) tuba tujya gusa n&rsquo;umukara kandi duhehereye aritwo dutanga ubutaka bwiza kandi bwera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uburyo utwo tubumbe tumeze biha ubutaka imiterere myiza yo gutuma buhumeka, buhitisha amazi, buhingika byoroshye, kutarekaho amazi n&rsquo;ibindi byinshi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ariko ikintu cy&rsquo;ingenzi cy&rsquo;utwo tubumbe n&rsquo;uko dufite ubushobozi bwo gukurura intungagihingwa (Nutrients)urugero nk&rsquo;iyo dushyizemo ifumbire mvaruganda. Bikoze nk&rsquo;uko muzi rukuruzi zikora kimwe gikurura ikindi (charges + .-). Ubu buryo bwo gufata izi ntungabutaka nibwo butuma ifumbire ishobora gutinda mu butaka igihe kirekire indi ntitindemo .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uburyo rero igihingwa gifata ibigitunga buturuka ku buryo utwo tubumbe tuboneka mu butaka ndetse na twa dusimba dutuma habaho imborera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imborera (Humus) irekura buhoro buhoro intungagihingwa . Ariko hari ibihingwa bikenera intungagihingwa nyinshi ndetse bikenera Azote nyinshi mu gihe biri gukura. Bikenera rero ikintu kibyunganira mu kubona intungagihingwa mu gihe birimo kuzana imbuto cg bitangiye kuyanga. Ibindi bihingwa nk&rsquo;amashu byo bikenera intungagihingwa nyinshi buri gihe .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uburyo bwiza rero bwo guha inyongera ibi bihingwa bikenera intungagihingwa nyinshi ni ugukoresha ifumbire isukika wikoreye wowe ubwawe mu rugo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyi fumbire iba ifite akarusho ko kuba ikoze mu bimera bivuzeko nta ngaruka izagira ku buzima bw&rsquo;udusimba tuba mu butaka tumwe twavuze hejuru ndetse ntinatume ubutaka busharira nk&rsquo;uko bigenda iyo dukoresheje ifumbire ikorewe mu nganda .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uburyo iyi fumbire ikorwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubu rero ni ubryo bwo gukora iyo fumbire iwawe mu rugo:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Igihingwa cya mbere gikoreshwa ni Igisura (<em>urtica dioica) </em>. Iki gitanga intungabihingwa nyinshi kandi gishobora no gukoreshwa nk&rsquo;umuti ukomeye wo kwica udukoko twangiza ibihingwa(pesticide). Ariko kandi igisura kigira Fosifore nke.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/07/igisura.jpg\"><img alt=\"igisura\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-175\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/07/igisura.jpg\" style=\"height:204px; width:250px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Igisura</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugirango ukore ifumbire ikungahaye kuri Fosifore (Phosphorus) ukoresha Ikicamahirwe cyangwa Kimbazi(Tithonia). Iki ni icyatsi gikora igihuru kimera ahantu henshi ariko kirimeza kandi ukabona kibangamiye imyaka gikunze kugira indabyo z&rsquo;umuhondo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Tithonia_diversifolia\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-174\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/07/tithonia_diversifolia.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225\" style=\"height:225px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Icyicamahirwe(Tithonia)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikindi gihingwa gikoreshwa cyane ni <em>Symphytum </em>iki kikaba gikungahaye kuri Potasium ndetse na Vitamini B12 ituma iyo ugemuye igihingwa imizi ihita ikura vuba kigafata aho ugiteye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Symphytum Officinale\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-173\" src=\"https://yeanrwanda.files.wordpress.com/2015/07/symphytum-officinale.jpg?w=300&amp;h=208\" style=\"height:208px; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Symphytum</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugirango utangire gukora ifumbire yawe ukenera indobo, umuhoro ndetse n&rsquo;igiti cyo kuvangisha.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Kusanya ibibabi bya kimwe muri ibi bhingwa twavuze haruguru.</li>\r\no<li>Numara kubitemagura ubiciyemo uduce ubishyire muri ya ndobo maze ushyiremo ibishishwa by&rsquo;amagi kugirango wongere Calcium izaba iri mw&rsquo;ifumbire yawe.</li>\r\no<li>Nurangiza wuzuze indobo amazi kugirango bya byatsi byose bizabe biri mu mazi.</li>\r\no<li>Pfundikira indobo neza ku buryo amasazi n&rsquo;imibu bitinjiramo ariko ukore ku buryo umwuka winjira ukanasohoka.</li>\r\no<li>Vangavanga iyo mvange kenshi ku munsi kugirango hanjyemo umwuka uhagije. Iyo mvange izatangira kuzana urufuro hejuru no kunuka mo gake nk&rsquo;ibintu byaboze. Iki ni ikimenyetso kiza kikubwirako ifumbire yawe itangiye gukoreka.</li>\r\no<li>Nyuma y&rsquo;ibyumweru bibiri cyangwa bitatu bya byatsi byose bizaba byahindutse amazi ibisigaye bikomeye bimeze nk&rsquo;ibyondo.</li>\r\no<li>Ibyo bigikomeye bikuremo ukoresheje igiti maze ya mazi asigaye uyayungurure ukoresheje akayunguruzo .</li>\r\no<li>Bizaba bisa n&rsquo;icyatsi gikeye kandi nta rufuro bifite.</li>\r\no<li>Ushobora kubika iyo fumbire ahantu hapfundikiye neza kugeza igihe uzayikenerera.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uburyo ikoreshwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kugirango uyikoreshe rero , uzashyira litiro imwe y&rsquo;iyo fumbire kuri litiro 10 z&rsquo;amazi (1:10), iyi fumbire ihita ishyirwa ku gihingwa iruhande ku mizi. Ushobora kuyishyiraho buri cyumweru .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ushobora kandi no kuyikoresha ku mababi ufuhera . Aha rero bizagusaba kuyiyungurura neza ukoresheje umwenda ku buryo ibitepfu byose bishiramo kugirango bitakwangiriza ipombo cyangwa ikindi gikoresho uri gukoresha ufuhera ku mababi. Muri iki gihe ho uvanga ukoresheje litiro imwe y&rsquo;ifumbire kuri litiro 20 z&rsquo;amazi (1:20).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ubu bushakashatsi tubukesha Anja Weber umuyobozi mukuru wa SoilCares Limited</em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n",
