        "title": "Tumenye uko Icyayi gihingwa n'uburyo cyitabwaho mumurima",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "icyayi2.jpg",
        "text": "<p>Ushobora kwibaza uti icyayi ni igihingwa gihingwa hehe? Hamwe nibindi bibazo byose waba wibazaga ku gihingwa cy&rsquo;icyayi uraza kubisubizwa muri iyi nkuru.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Icyayi rero ni igihingwa gikunda mu turere dukonja kandi tugwisha imvura ihagije, iki gihingwa kandi gikunda ubutaka bw&rsquo;isi ndende kandi bufite imborera ihagije. Icyayi ni igihngwa kigira amoko menshi yigajemo BWG/5, 31/11, BB/35, BB/10 n&rsquo;ayandi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Menya uko bategura umurima w&rsquo;iki gihingwa, mu mirimo yibandwaho mu gutegura umurima wo guhingamo icyayo harimo kurwanya isuri, guhinga umurima ndetse nogucukura imyobo. Iyo umurima umaze guhingwa urafumbirwa hakoreshejwe 60kg z&rsquo;ivumbire mvaruganda ya N.P.K 25.5.5 ku giti kimwe ingemwe zimaze gufata.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ingemwe ziterwa hakoreshejwe ingemwe 105 kuri are 1 batera kuri 130cm hagati y&rsquo;imirongo na 75cm ku mirongo. Kuri Ha batera ingemwe 10500 hagati y&rsquo;Ukwakira n&rsquo;Ukuboza iyo ari imusozi naho mu gishanga ni hagati ya Gashyantare na Werurwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kimwe nibindi bihingwa icyayi nacyo kigomba gukorerwa imirimo nko kubagarwa, kugomorora amazi mu murima, gusasira, gutera ibiti bihagarika umuyaga, gukata icyayi, gusimbura ingemwe za pfuye no kurwanya indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tumenye indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi by&rsquo;iki gihingwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><strong>Indwara y&rsquo;ububobere: </strong>iyi ndwara uyibwira nuko ikihingwa gikura buhoro buhoro cyane, amababi ahinduka umuhondo nyuma akarabirana kugeza ubwo igiti n&rsquo;imizi byose byuma bikabora. Imizi minini n&rsquo;igice cyo hasi y&rsquo;igihimba birasaduka. Hagati mu busate n&rsquo;imbere mu ruhu haza uruhumbu rwera. Kuyirwanya ni ugutwika icyayi cyafashwe n&rsquo;iyi ndwara.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa: </strong>Iyo ibishyitsi by&rsquo;amashyamba cy&rsquo;ibyo mu mirwanyasuri bisigaye mu mirima bitaranduwe, bituma kenshi na kenshi indwra ikura igafata icyayi. Iyo ndwara iboneka cyane mu mu butaka buremereye kandi buhehereye.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\no<li><strong>Indwara y&rsquo;ibidomo by&rsquo;ibijuju: </strong>iyi ndwara ifata ku mababi bikaba ibidomo by&rsquo;ikigina n&rsquo;igicucu, bifite ishusho rijya gusa nk&rsquo;uruziga naho hagati y&rsquo;ibidomo yajya kweruruka naho k&rsquo;umuzenguruko wacyo harijimye. Kuyirwanya ni ukwirinda icyatuma icyayi gikura nabi, kwirinda gukoresha ifumgire y&rsquo;Azote nyinshi, gukata icyayi neza no kuyisasira ku gihe, iyo bibaye muri pipiniyeri hakorshwa umuti wa Mancozeb (Dithan M45)</li>\r\no<li><strong>Agatagangurira k&rsquo;umutuku: </strong>ni agakoko gato (mm 0.5) iyo gakuze kagira ibara ritukura, ibyana, udukuru bitungwa no konona icyayi iyo tumaze gukura tunyunyuza amazi yo mu mababi, amababi yafashwe ahinduka ikigina kijya gutukura. Iyi ndwara irwanywa hakoreshejwe umuti wa Dimenthroate.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitondekwa: </strong>iyo ukoresheje uyu muti wa Dimentroate icyayi gisoromwa nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 15</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Menya neza uko basarura nuko babika icyayi cyeze, </strong>basarura ibibabi uko iminsi 7 ishize kugeza ku minsi 15, umusaruro ushobora kuboneka ni toni 3.5 na 7.5 kuri Ha1 z&rsquo;icyayi cyumye neza ku mwaka. Iyo icyayi kimaze gutunganyirizwa neza mu nganda, icyayi cyumye neza gishyirwa mu bisanguku byabugenewe bikarindwa ubukonje.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Byakusanyijwe na Jean Luc Mugiran</em><em>eza hifashishijwe ibitabo by&rsquo;imfashanyigisho bya Minagri na RAB</em></p>\r\n",
