        "id": 193,
        "title": "Uburyo bwo guhinga Kawa n,uburyo yitabwaho igahtanga umusaruro mwiza",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "kawa.jpg",
        "text": "<p>Ikawa ubusanzwe ni igihingwa gikunda guhingwa mu turere tw&rsquo;ubuhinzi, Ikawa kandi ikunda guhingwa mu nyengero z&rsquo;Ikivu no mu murambi wo hagati mu karre k&rsquo;urusekabuye. Ikawa ni igihingwa gikunga ubutaka bwiza, burebure, buhehereye kandi budakomeye cyane. Ikawa ni gihngwa kigira amoko menshi cyane arimo <strong>Harrar, Jackson 2/1257, BM 71, BM 139 </strong>nayandi&hellip;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko bategura pipiniyeri: </strong>Bahumbika imbuto mu kwezi k&rsquo;Ukwakira n&rsquo;Ugushyingo kandi kg 1 y&rsquo;imbuto itanga ingemwe ziri hagati ya 2500 na 3000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko bategura umurima: </strong>imirimo ikorwa harimo kurwanya isuri, gukuraho ibihuru no gutema imizi, gucukura imyobo ya 60cm z&rsquo;ubugari kuri 60cm z&rsquo;uburebure n 80cm z&rsquo;ubujyakuzimu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko bafumbira umurima wo guhingamo Ikawa: </strong>bashyira kg 20 z&rsquo;ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera iboze neza kuri buri giti, imvura igatangira kugwa muri Werurwe na Nzeri, icyo gihingwa bagiha kandi gr 400 za NPK 20.10.10 mu byiciro bibiri. Ku butaka bukarishye cyane ni ngombwa ko umuhinzi ashyiramo kg 1cy&rsquo;ishwagara buri myaka itatu, ni ngombwa kandi gutera ibiti ndumburabutaka mu murima uteyemo igihingwa cya Kawa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko batera ingemwe: </strong>haterwa ingemwe 2500 kuri Ha hakoreshejwe m 2 hagati y&rsquo;umurongo n&rsquo;undi na m 2 hagati y&rsquo;urugemwe n&rsquo;urundi ku murongo umwe. Batera Kawa mu kwezi k&rsquo;Ukwakira n&rsquo;Ugushyiingo naho gusimbura ingemwe zapfuye muri Werurwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gufata neza Kawa mu murima: </strong>ni ngombwa kubagara, kwirinda gukomeretsa imizi ya Kawa, ni itegeko gusasira Kawa hakoreshejwe Temeda, Setariya, Ibirere n&rsquo;ibindi bishishwa biboneka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukata kawa:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><strong>Kugonda Kawa: </strong>kawa ziba zimaze amezi 10 zitewe hagamijwe kuzatereka amashami atatu kuri buri giti. Iryo kata baryita: <strong>ikata ritereka Kawa</strong></li>\r\no<li><strong>Ikara ryongera umusaruro: </strong>Buri mwaka amashami yo hasi atacyera yumye agomba gukatwa.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Ikata ryo gusazura igipimo: </strong>Bikorwa hagati y&rsquo;imyaka 5 cyangwa 7 kawa itanga umusaruro. Ku mwaka wa mbere w&rsquo;iri katwa hatemwa ibiti bibiri nyuma y&rsquo;isarura (muri Nyakanga na Kanama) hagasigara igiti kimwe, ku mwaka wa kabiri w&rsquo;iri katwa batema igiti cya 3 cyari gisigaye, ibyo biti bitemwa hamaze gutoranywa ibishibu bitatu bifite cm 50.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kurwanya indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi bya Kawa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>a) Agasurira: </strong>ni agakoko gafite ibara ry&rsquo;umuhondo n&rsquo;umukara nibara ry&rsquo;uburu bujya kuba icyatsi kunda no ku mugongo, iyo utwo dukoko utwiciye ku nda turanuka. Iki cyonnyi bakirwanya batera umuti wa Chloropyriphas ehtly w&rsquo;amazi, uyu muti ugomba guterwa ku gihe kandi hamwe, batera inshuro 2 birangije ibyumweru bibiri, bavanga ml 22.5 na litiro 15 z&rsquo;amazi hanyum iyo mvange igaterwa ku biti hafo 40.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Indwara z&rsquo;ingenzi: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li><strong>a) Akaribata: </strong>ni indwara iterwa n&rsquo;udukoko duto cyane twitwa<strong> &ldquo; Colletotricum coffeatum&rdquo; </strong>ikawa yafashwe niyi ndwara igaragaza imbuto z&rsquo;amabara ahombanye aho yafashe, zikagera nubwo zibora cyangwa zigahinduka umukara, amababi y&rsquo;igiti cyafashwe amera nkayababutse, ururrabo n&rsquo;intete bikumira ku giti rimwe na rimwe amashami akuma imitwe. Iyi ndwara irwanywa hakoreshejwe umuti wa Oxychlorure de cuivre inshuro 7 kugeza kuri 11 bitewe n&rsquo;ubwinshi bw&rsquo;imvura, haterwa gr 400 bavanga na litiro 20 z&rsquo;amazi batera ibiti hafo 25 bakagenda birenza iminsi 15, batangira gutera umuti hashize ukwezi kumwe kawa zirabije. Btera umuti mu kwezi kwa Nzeri, Ukwakira, Ugushyingo, Ukuboza na Gashyantare (iyo imvura yatangiye kugwa) no muri Werurwe, Mata na Gicurasi (iyo imvura ikigwa)</li>\r\no<li><strong>b) Umugese:</strong> iyi ndwara iterwa n&rsquo;uduhumyo duto bita Hemileia vastatrix, igaragazwa nuko mu mababi hasi hazahi ifu y&rsquo;umuhondo isa n&rsquo;agakungugu kajya gusa n&rsquo;icunga rihishije. Ikunda kugaragara cyane mu gihe cy&rsquo;ubushyuhe, cyane cyane mu mpera z&rsquo;itumba no mu ntangiriro z&rsquo;impeshyi. Iyi ndwara nayo irwanywa hakoreshejwe umuti wa Oxychlorure de cuivre, bavanga gr 70 na litiro 20 z&rsquo;amazi batera ku biti hafi 25, batera 1 mu kwezi (Nzeri-ukwakira-Ugushyingo- Ukuboza, iyo imvura Werurwe, Mata na Gicurasi)</li>\r\no<li><strong>c) Indwara ya Gikongoro: </strong>Ni indwara yitwa <strong>&ldquo;Die-Back&rdquo; </strong>iterwa n&rsquo;umukeno, ikunze gufata kawa ziteye ku butaka bubi, izadakomeye ndetse ni zeze cyane ariko zitabonye ifumbire ihagije. Uyibwirwa nuko imbuto zihisha imburagihe maze zikirabura nyuma zikumva, amababi nayo aruma ahereye ku mutwe. Uburyo bwo gukurwanya iyi ndwara ni uguhinga kawa mu butaka bwiza, gusukura kawa neza, gufumbira neza kandi kugihe, gusasira neza kandi ku gihe.</li>\r\no<li><strong>d) Serikosiporiyoze: </strong>iyi ndwara iterwa n&rsquo;uduhumyo duto cyane, igakara cyane iyo ifite ingufu nke, ikunda kugaragara cyane ahantu hadafite azoti ihagije. Ku mababi hazaho amabara y&rsquo;ikigina. Bayirwanya batera umuti wa Oxychlrorure de cuivre gr 20 muri litiro 10 z&rsquo;amazi no gukorsha amafumbire arimo azoti (nka ure 46%)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Umusaruro: </strong>kawa yerera hagati y&rsquo;imyaka 2 na 3, kawa isarurwa yeze neza igahita ijyanwa ku ruganda rutunganya ibitumbwe kugirango uruganda rubashe kuyihera neza, kuyironga no kuyanika ku meza asukuye neza kandi kuzuba riringaniye kuburyo kawa itarenza 12% z&rsquo;ububobere. Umusaruro ushobora kuboneka uri hagati ya kg 750 na toni 2500 yumye bitewe ni imihingire ya kawa. Kawa isaruwe igomba kurara igemuwe ku ruganda rutonora kuko ari kuri uwo murimo umuhinzi ugarukira.</p>\r\n",
