        "id": 198,
        "title": "Uburyo bwo guhinga imiteja bwa kijyambere",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "imiteja.png",
        "text": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ubuhinzi bw&rsquo;imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo ni ubuhinzi bushobora kwitabirwa na buri wese kuko imirimo yabwo yoroshye. Imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo ni igihingwa kiri mu muryango w&rsquo;ibinyamisogogwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aho imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo ikunda</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo ishobora guhingwa mu Rwanda hose. Ariko aho ikunda cyane ni ahari imiterere ikurikira:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Ubushyuhe buri hagati ya dogere 20 kugeza kuri 25</li>\r\no<li>ubutumburuke buri hagati ya metero 1000 kugeza kuri metero 2100</li>\r\no<li>Imvura igwa ku gipimo kiri hagati ya mirimetero 900 na mirimetero 1200 Ubutaka Imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo ihingwa mu butaka butarimo amazi menshi kandi bufite ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera ihagije n&rsquo;ubusharire bw&rsquo;ubutaka buri hagati ya 6.5 &ndash; 7.5</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amoko y&rsquo;Imiteja y&rsquo;Ibishyimbo Hari amako menshi y&rsquo;imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Imiteja irandaranda</li>\r\no<li>Imiteja migufi</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Ariko amoko akenerwa ku masoko mpuzamahanga ni aya akurikira: monel, vernadon, gloria, claudia supper monel, espadia, morgan. Irandaranda hari nka Kentucky wonder.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ikigero cy&rsquo;imbutobatera </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyo utera ibishyimbo by&rsquo;imiteja ukenera imbuto ingana n&rsquo;ibiro 50 kugeza ku biro 60 kuri hegitari Imwe. Ku miteja yera irandaranda hakenerwa ibiro 25 kugeza kuri 30 kuri hegitare imwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Igihe cyogutera imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Igihe ufite uburyo bwo kuvomerera imyaka ushobora gutera imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo buri gihe cyose mu mwaka. Mu gihe cy&rsquo;ihinga gisanzwe imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo ishobora guterwa; ariko mu gihe cy&rsquo;imvura nyinshi ukirinda kuyitera mu gishanga kuko itihanganira imvura nyinshi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ingero zikurizwa mubuhinzi bw&rsquo;imiteja</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Hagati y&rsquo;umurongo n&rsquo;undi hajya centimetero 60 kugeza 70 cm</li>\r\no<li>Haterwa imbuto imwe mu mwobo ufite ubujyakuzimu bwa cm 15</li>\r\no<li>Hagati y&rsquo;imbuto n&rsquo;indi hajya centimetero 5 kugeza ku 10</li>\r\no<li>Umutabo ugomba kuba ufite metero 1.5</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingano y&rsquo;ifumbire ikenerwa </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo ikenera ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera iboze neza ingana na toni icumi kuri hegitare imwe (10/ha).Iyo ifumbire iterwa ivangwa n&rsquo;ubutaka neza mbere yo gutera. Mu gihe k&rsquo;itera ry&rsquo;imbuto hakenerwa kandi ifumbire mvaruganda ingana n&rsquo;ibiro 200 bya DAP kuri hegitare imwe, ikavangwa neza n&rsquo;ubutaka mbere yo gushyira imbuto mu butaka. Igihe ibishyimbo by&rsquo;imiteja bitangiye kuzana amababi ya mbere hakoreshwa ifumbire ya CAN ingana n&rsquo;ibiro 100 kuri hegitare imwe, ikaba kandi yatangira gukoreshwa igihe ibishyimbo by&rsquo;imiteja bitangiye kuzana ururabo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gukenura igihingwa cy&rsquo;imiteja. </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo ibagarwa bwa mbere nyuma y&rsquo;ibyumweru 2 kugeza kuri 3 itewe. Mu kubagara witondera guhungabanya imizi y&rsquo;igihingwa. Kubagara bwa kabiri bishobora gukorwa nyuma y&rsquo;ibindi by&rsquo;umweru 2 kugeza kuri 3, ibagarwa rya mbere ribaye. Wirinda kubagara igihe imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo itangiye kuzana indabyo. Igihe ufite imirima minini ugamije gukora ubuhinzi bubyara inyungu, igihe imirima ifite urwiri rwinshi ushobora gukoresha imiti ya herbicides ku buryo bukurikira:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Lasso 4 EC (alahlor) : litiro 3 z&rsquo;umuti zivangwa muri litiro 400 z&rsquo;amazi bigakoreshwa kuri hegitari imwe.</li>\r\no<li>Stamp (Pendimethalin) : litiro 2.5 z&rsquo;umuti zivangwa muri litiro 400 z&rsquo;amazi kuri hegitari imwe. Igihe hari urwiri rukabije ushobora gukoresha Basagram(bentazon) hakoreshwa litiro 2.5kugeza kuri 3 kuri hegitari imwe.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Iminsi Imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo isarurirwaho</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo itangira gusarurwa hagati y&rsquo;iminsi 42 n&rsquo;iminsi 56 igakomeza gusarurwa kugeza hagati y&rsquo;ukwezi kumwe n&rsquo;igice kugeza ku mezi abiri.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Umurumbuko</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyo imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo yitaweho neza ishobora gutanga umusaruro ungana na toni 4 kugeza kuri 8 kuri hegitari imwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko umusaruro witabwaho</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gusarura imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo bikorwa mu gihe hatari imvura nyinshi, iyo usarura imiteja ishyirwa mu gikoresho cya pulasitike cyumutse neza. Abasarura bagomba kuba bafite isuku ku myambaro ndetse no ku mubiri, mu gihe biyemeje gukora ubuhinzi bubyara inyungu. Iyo basarura imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo batoranya imeze neza idakomeretse, itarariwe n&rsquo;udusimba, ifite umubyimba ugororotse utigonzagonze wa mm 6 kugeza kuri mm 9; n&rsquo;uburebure bwa cm10.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko babika Imitejay&rsquo;Ibishyimbo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyo wifuza kohereza Imiteja y&rsquo;ibishyimbo kw&rsquo; isoko mpuzamahanga ukurikiza ibyavuzwe haruguru byose. Mu kuyibika bayishyira mu makarito y&rsquo;ibiro 3 cyangwa mu bikoresho bya pulasitike bipima kuva ku magarama 250; 500 kugeza ku kiro kimwe. Ibikwa ahantu hari ubukonje buri hagati ya dogeri 7 kugeza ku 8 n&rsquo;ubuhehere bwa 95% kugeza kuri 100% mu gihe kingana n&rsquo;icyumweru kugeza ku byumweru 2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Icyitonderwa : Ibi bipimo tubaha bishobora guhinduka bitewe n&rsquo;iterambere rigenda rigerwaho mu buhinzi cg bitewe n&rsquo;imiterere y&rsquo;ubutaka uhinga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Tubikesha icyahoze ari RHODA (Rwanda Horticulture Development Authority )</em></p>\r\n",
