        "id": 202,
        "title": "Ibinyomoro: indwara ndetse n'ibyonnyi by'ibinyomoro",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "ibinyomoro2.png",
        "text": "<p>Mu nkuru zacu ziheruka tabagejejeho <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.wordpress.com/2015/06/23/ibinyomoro-uburyo-bwo-kubihinga-kuva-mu-murama-kugera-ku-musaruro-ujya-kwisoko/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">uburyo bwo guhinga kijyambere ibinyomoro</span></a> , hari benshi badusabye kubashakira ibijyanye n&rsquo;indwara ndetse n&rsquo;ibyonnyi by&rsquo;ibinyomoro niyo mpamvu uyu munsi tubigarutseho mu buryo burambuye nk&rsquo;uko tubikesha NEAB ku rubuga rwayo. Tugiye rero kubibaramburira ubwo abahinzi b&rsquo;ibinyomoro ni ahabo ndetse nundi wese wifuza gukora uyu mushinga.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n\t<li>MILIDIYU Y&rsquo;IFU (Powedery mildew)<br />\r\n\tIKIYITERA<br />\r\n\tNi indwara iterwa n&rsquo;uduhumyo twitwa Erysiphe sp., Oidium sp. Ishobora gutuma amababi yose akokoka ku giti agashiraho iyo itarwanyijwe. Igaragara cyane ku kibabi hejuru, ku ruti ruto, ku mutwe w&rsquo;igihingwa, ku ndabo, no ku mbuto.<br />\r\n\tIBIMENYETSO<br />\r\n\tIyi ndwara igaragazwa n&rsquo;ibibara bimeze nk&rsquo;ivu by&rsquo;ikijuju. Indabo zibanza kuba umuhondo nyuma zikuma, zikaba umukara zigapfa. Amababi yafashwe ashobora kuba umuhondo kandi akikunja, naho intimatima y&rsquo;igihingwa ntibumbure.<br />\r\n\tUKO BAYIRWANYA<br />\r\n\tGukoresha umuti wica uduhumyo urimo sulfure.<br />\r\n\tKutegeranya ibinyomoro mu gihe cy&rsquo;itera.<br />\r\n\tKutavomera cyane.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">Hari ibihugu bakoresha igice cya litiro y&rsquo;amata avanze na litiro enye n&rsquo;igice z&rsquo;amazi bagatera ku gihingwa kirwaye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">2. INDA/ UDUHUNDUGURU (Aphids)<br />\r\nInda ni udukoko tubamo amoko menshi atandukanwa n&rsquo;amabara yatwo. Izwi cyane mu binyomoro ni inda y&rsquo;icyatsi (Myzus persicae).<br />\r\nZikunze kugaragara munsi y&rsquo;amababi no ku ruti by&rsquo;igihingwa cy &lsquo;ikinyomoro. Ziboneka igihe cyose ariko cyane cyane mu gihe cy&rsquo;izuba.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">UKO ZANGIZA<br />\r\nInda inyunyuza imyunyu n&rsquo;amazi mu gihingwa. Zikwirakwiza indwara za virusi z&rsquo;igihingwa zikanashyira umushongi ku mababi ukurura uduhumyo dufata muri uwo mushongi ugasanga amababi atwikiriwe ntabeho neza akaba yakuma akagwa.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">IBIMENYETSO<br />\r\nTiripusi yangiza mu gihe cy&rsquo;izuba. Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara ni tiripusi zitera amagi mu mababi akaremererwa. Zirya amababi agasigara yerurutse. Ku mbuto aho tiripusi yariye hamera nk&rsquo;ahakobotse hakaba ikigina.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">UKO ZANGIZA<br />\r\nIbishorobwa birya amababi agasigara abonerana, Tiripusi n&rsquo;ibishorobwa byazo byona birundanije ku mababi bikarya amababi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">IBIMENYETSO<br />\r\nVirusi izwi cyane ni mozayike (Tamarillo mosaic virus; TaMV) ituma urubuto ruzaho ibibara byerurutse, ku mababi hakazaho ibibara by&rsquo;umuhondo.<br />\r\nIzindi virusi twavuga ni nka &ldquo;cucumber mosaic virus&rdquo; itera kugwingira kw&rsquo;igihingwa amababi akazaho ibibara. &ldquo;potato virus Y&rdquo; ituma ku mbuto hazaho ibibara by&rsquo;umukara n&rsquo;umusaruro ukagabanuka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">UKO BAZIRWANYA</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Gutera imiti nka Dim&eacute;thoate irwanya udukoko.</li>\r\n\t<li>Gusura umurima byibuze kabiri mu cyumweru.</li>\r\n\t<li>Gukuraho amababi ashaje umurima ukinjiramo urumuri n&rsquo;umwuka.</li>\r\n\t<li>Kugenzura niba nta nshishi zigaragara ku giti kuko zishobora kuba zikuruwe n&rsquo;umushongi w&rsquo;inda.</li>\r\n\t<li>Kudakoresha ifumbire irimo azote nyinshi.</li>\r\n\t<li>Gukoresha amasabune arimo umuti wica udukoko, cyangwa amavuta y&rsquo;igiti cya neem.</li>\r\n\t<li>Kuvomera n&rsquo;amazi afite ingufu.</li>\r\n\t<li>Kugenzura umurima n&rsquo;iruhande rwawo niba nta nda zihari mbere yo gutera ibinyomoro.</li>\r\n\t<li>Kudahohotera udusimba turya inda nk&rsquo;udusurira n&rsquo;amavubi.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>3. ISAZI Y&rsquo;UMWERU (Whitefly)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Isazi y&rsquo;umweru ni agasimba kareshya na mm 1 gasa umuhondo kakagira amababa y&rsquo;umweru.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UKO YANGIZA<br />\r\nIyo sazi inyunyuza imyunyu n&rsquo;amazi by&rsquo;igihingwa kandi isiga umushongi umeze nk&rsquo;ubuki ku mababi no ku mbuto bigatuma imbuto zisa nabi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UKO BAYIRWANYA</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Kugenzura umurima kenshi havanwa ibibabi bishaje n&rsquo;ibiriho isazi nyinshi mu murima</li>\r\n\t<li>Gukoresha imitego ifite ibara ry&rsquo;umuhondo(rikurura izo sazi) irimo kole yo gufata izo sazi ishyirwa hejuru y&rsquo;amababi.</li>\r\n\t<li>Gukoresha imiti yica udukoko nka Dim&eacute;thoate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>4. TIRIPUSI (Thrips)<br />\r\nNi agasimba gato gashobora kugira uburebure bwa mm 1.25. Gafite ibara ry&rsquo;umuhondo. Ingabo igira amabara yerurutse kandi ari nto ugereranije n&rsquo;ingore.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UKO BAZIRWANYA</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Gukura ibyatsi bibi mu murima.</li>\r\n\t<li>Ubutaka bugomba guhingwa nyuma yo gusarura.</li>\r\n\t<li>Gusiga intera ihagije hagati y&rsquo;ibihingwa.</li>\r\n\t<li>Gukoresha imiti yica udukoko nka Dimethoateo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>5. VIRUSI Z&rsquo;IBINYOMORO<br />\r\nIgihingwa cy&rsquo;ibinyomoro kigira virusi nyinshi zituma gikura nabi, zikanatera amabara ku mbuto ibyo bikagabanya ubwiza n&rsquo;umusaruro wabyo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UKO BAZIRWANYA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nta miti ya virusi ihari, igikorwa mu kuzirwanya ni:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Kurandura ibiti byafashwe.</li>\r\n\t<li>Gufumbira igihingwa kikagira ingufu zo kwirwanaho.</li>\r\n\t<li>Kurwanya inda z&rsquo;ibihingwa n&rsquo;utundi dukoko tuguruka kuko dukwirakwiza izo ndwara</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
