        "title": "Uburyo bwo guhinga urusenda ku buryo bwa kijyambere",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "urusenda.png",
        "text": "<p><strong>Akamaro k&rsquo;urusenda</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nk&rsquo;uko RAB ibisobanura,urusenda ruraribwa. Rushobora kuribwa ari rubisi cyangwa rwumye. Bashobora no kurukoresha muri salade nk&rsquo;urusenda ruryohera,kuruteka,ndetse rushobora gukorwamo n&rsquo;ibindi bintu bitandukanye nka &raquo;hot pepper,ketchup,imiti n&rsquo;ibindi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uretse kuba indyoshyandyo,urusenda rufitiye akamaro kanini umubiri wacu,rutuma imyanya imwe n&rsquo;imwe yo mu kanwa no mu gifu ikora neza,n&rsquo;igogora ry&rsquo;ibiryo rikagenda neza. Hari n&rsquo;aho bavuga ko umuntu ufite amibe n&rsquo;ikibazo cyo mu mara &laquo; intestine worms &raquo;bamutegeka kurya urusenda. Urusenda kandi rukoreshwa no mu kwica udukoko dutandukanye dutera indwara mu bihingwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibigize urusenda</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bimwe mu bigize urusenda bishobora kugirira umubiri akamaro : ku magarama 100 y&rsquo;urusenda harimo garama 74 z&rsquo;amazi,ibitera imbaraga 395KJ,94Kcal, garama 4,1 za poroteyine, garama 2,3 z&rsquo;ibinyamavuta, garama 50 za kalisiyumu,n&rsquo;ibindi nka manyeziyumu na Feri.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Imiterere y&rsquo;urusenda</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urusenda ni igiti gishobora gukura kikaba cyagera kuri 2m z&rsquo;uburebure. Gifite amababi menshi kikaba gishobora kwera kabiri mu mwaka. Urusenda ruri mu bwoko bw&rsquo;ibinyamisogwe. Ubwoko bw&rsquo;umusogwe bwigaragaza bukurikijwe ubwoko bw&rsquo;urusenda :hari uruba icyatsi kibisi,umutuku,umuhondo n&rsquo;andi mabara atandukanye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urusenda rwo mu bwoko bwa Bushari &ldquo;chilli&rdquo;ni urusenda rwihuta mu mikurire yarwo,indabo zarwo ziba ziri hamwe z&rsquo;umweru rukagira imisogwe miremire ireshya na cm 2 kugeza kuri 16. Urwo ruratukura ,rukaba rushobora kuribwa ari rubisi cyangwa rwumishijwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aho urusenda rukunda</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urusenda rushobora guhingwa mu Rwanda hose ukurikije ubwoko bwarwo n&rsquo;imiterere y&rsquo;ikirere. Ariko ibigomba kwitabwaho cyane ni ibi bikurikira : Ubushyuhe buri hagati ya 15-25<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">0</span></sup>C, ubutumburuke bugera kuri m 2000 n&rsquo;imvura iri hagati ya 600mm -900mm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ubutaka ruhingwamo</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urusenda rushobora kwera u butaka bwose butarimo amazi menshi kandi bufite imyunyu ngugu ya ngombwa bukize no ku ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera. Ubusharire (pH) bw&rsquo;ubutaka bugomba kuba buri hagati ya 5,5 na 6,8.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amoko y&rsquo;urusenda</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hari amoko menshi y&rsquo;urusenda ariko ku masoko mpuzamahanga hakunzwe cyane aya akurikira : california wonder.Yolo wonder,Emirald giant na Bird&rsquo;s eye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ikigero cy&rsquo;imbuto batera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyo uteye utanyujije mu buhumbikiro ukoresha 1kg/ha. Iyo unyujije mu buhumbikiro ukenera 5kg/ha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ifumbire</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urusenda rukenera ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera iboze neza ingana na Toni 10 kuri 1ha. 10t/ha. Ifumbire mvaruganda ukoresha kg 250/ha ya TSP(triple super phosphate) bagitera. Iyo urusenda rumaze kugira cm 15, rukenera ibiro 100 bya CAN ( Calcium Ammonia Nitrate) kuri ha,naho nyuma y&rsquo;ukwezi rugakenera ibiro 200 bya CAN kuri ha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Igihe cyo gutera urusenda</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kimwe n&rsquo;ibindi bihingwa bica mu buhumbikiro,ingemwe z&rsquo;urusenda zitegurwa muri Kamena,naho kuzitera bikorwa muri Nzeli-Ukwakira.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uburyo bwo gutubura ingemwe z&rsquo;urusenda</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kwinaza</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aho winariza urusenda hagomba gutegurwa neza nk&rsquo;uko bisanzwe ku zindi mboga zibanza kunyuzwa mu buhumbikiro. Mu buhumbikiro urusenda ruterwa kuri cm 20 hagati y&rsquo;umurongo n&rsquo;undi. Ubuhumbikiro bugomba gutwikirwa kugira ngo burindwe imvura n&rsquo;izuba,bugakurwaho ibirindazuba mbere y&rsquo;icyumweru kimwe ngo ingemwe zigemurwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kugemura</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Urusenda rugemurwa nibura rumaze kugira amababi 8 kugeza ku 10. Ni ukuvuga hashize iminsi iri hagati ya 30 na 40. Bagemura batoranya ingemwe zimeze neza zikomeye,bigakorwa mu gitondo izuba ritarava cyangwa nimugoroba rimaze kurenga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gutegura umurima</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umurima ugomba gutegurwa neza,utabiye neza kugeza nibura muri cm 30. Ugashyiramo ifumbire kandi hakurikijwe ingero z&rsquo;ifumbire zatanzwe hejuru.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uburyo bukoreshwa mu gutera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Urusenda ruterwa ku buryo bukurikira</strong> :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Basiga cm 40 hagati y&rsquo;ingeri n&rsquo;indi cyangwa hagati y&rsquo;igiti cy&rsquo;urusenda n&rsquo;ikindi.Iyo uteye utanyujije mu buhumbikiro,usiga cm 30 hagati y&rsquo;intete n&rsquo;indi,ugasiga cm 70 hagati y&rsquo;umurongo n&rsquo;undi. Urusenda ruterwa kuri cm 60 hagati y&rsquo;umurongo n&rsquo;undi. Mu murima wa hegitali imwe ,hahingwamo ingemwe ziri hagati y&rsquo;ibihumbi 50 na 80. Ubutaha tuzabagezaho ibyonnyi n&rsquo;indwara z&rsquo;urusenda.</p>\r\n",
