        "title": "Ibitunguru (Onyo): Tekiniki zo kubihinga kijyambere",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "ibitunguru g.png",
        "text": "<ol>\r\no<li><strong>Umuryango w&rsquo;ibihingwa :</strong> ibitunguru &laquo; ALLIUM CEPA &raquo; kimwe na puwalo, <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.wordpress.com/2015/04/12/tumenye-uko-bahinga-tungurusumu/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">tungurusumu</span></a> bibarirwa mu muryango wa &laquo; Liliaceae &raquo; muri ordre ya Liliflores no mu muryango mugari wa &laquo; Monocotyledones &raquo;</li>\r\no<li><strong>Aho bikunda</strong> : bikunda mu Rwanda hose. Ariko kugirango ibijumba bibe binini, hagomba uburebure bw&rsquo;umunsi mugufi buri hagati y&rsquo;amasaha 12 na 16. Hagomba kandi ubushyuhe buri hejuru ya dogere 18 (18&deg;C) kugirango ibitunguru bibyimbe bimere nk&rsquo;ibihaze. Ubushyuhe buke bwo bubifasha mu gihe cyo gushibuka, gukura no kuzana indabo.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Ubutaka:</strong> Onyo ikunda ubutaka bworoshye, butari burebure cyane kandi bwumutse neza. Ntabwo ikunda ubutaka buhora butose kandi n&rsquo;ubutaka bw&rsquo;ibumba si bwiza. Ikunda ubutaka burimo potasi. Niyo mpamvu, umuhinzi agomba kubufumbiza ivu.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Amoko :</strong> Amoko yamamazwa mu Rwanda ni aya :</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; igitunguru gitukura : Red Cl&eacute;ole</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; igitunguru cy&rsquo;umuhondo : Texas grano</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ayo moko afite amabara atandukanye. Niyo mpamvu umuhinzi areba ibara n&rsquo;impumuro (parfum) y&rsquo;ubwoko agiye guhinga kuko aribyo abaguzi bakunze kwibandaho.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\no<li><strong>Ifumbire :</strong> kubera ko ifumbire ari ingirakamaro mu gutunganya imiterere y&rsquo;ubutaka, ni ngombwa gushyiramo ifumbire iboze neza cyane. Kg 200/are 1 iba ihagije.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Igihe cy&rsquo;ihinga :-</strong> kwinaza muri pepiniyeri : Mata-Kamena</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; bihingwa (kugemura) mu mpeshyi ariko bikavomerwa. Bigomba gutangira kwera mbere y&rsquo;imvura yo mu kwezi kwa Nzeri</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\no<li><strong>Gutera ibitunguru : </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Habanza kwinaza umurama mu buhumbikiro bakoresha g 5/m&sup2; 1. Bataba umurama muri mm 5-10 ku mirongo bagasigamo cm 10 hagati yayo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Urwinarizo rufite m&sup2; 100 rurahagije kugirango ubone ingemwe zahinga ha 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Igihe bimara mu rwinarizo : iminsi 45 kugeza kuri 60</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Bagemura onyo ifite umubyimba w&rsquo;igice cyo hasi ungana n&rsquo;ikaramu nto, icyo gihe amababi aba areshya na cm 15-20</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Uko bagemura : mbere yo gutera ingemwe, babanza gushabura iminsi y&rsquo;ingemwe, itemerwa kuri cm 1 hepfo y&rsquo;ikijumba cya onyo kandi ntibakuraho imitwe y&rsquo;amababi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Bazitera kuri cm 20-25 hagati y&rsquo;imirongo na cm 5-10 ku mirongo ni ukuvuga ingemwe 450.000/ha</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Urugemwe ruterwa kuri cm 3 z&rsquo;ibujyakuzimu, nyuma bamara gutera bagasubiranya kandi bagatsindagira itaka ryo hejuru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Iyo ushaka ibitunguru bitari binini kuko aribyo bibikika, utera ingemwe nyinshi/are</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"8\">\r\no<li><strong>Gukorera ibitunguru : </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Kubagara kenshi ariko unamenera kugirango ubutaka bworohe no kugirango ibyatsi bidakura vuba bigakwirakwiza indwara</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Iyo onyo itangiye kubyibuha, bataba ivu iruhande rwayo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Kwambura ibijumba by&rsquo;ibitunguru ubutaka kugirango bishobore kubyimba no gufata ibara.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bikorwa ibitunguru biri hafi yo kwera babanza kubigondera amababi ku munigo wayo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(collet).</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"9\">\r\no<li><strong>Indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi : </strong><strong>a) Isazi ya onyo : </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikiyitera : isazi y&rsquo;ibitunguru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aho ifata : igihingwa cyose</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibimenyetso : amababi aratumba. Inyo ziyo sazi zica utuyira mu gitunguru maze kikabora kikananuka cyane</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uko bayirwanya :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; kurandura no gutwikira mu mwobo ibitunguru byafashwe</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; kuvanga onyo na karoti kuko karoti yirukana isazi ifata onyo, naho onyo ikirukana ifata karoti</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; aho isazi yageze, nta onyo igomba gusubira muri uwo murima mbere y&rsquo;imyaka 3</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\" type=\"a\">\r\no<li><strong>Ububore bw&rsquo;umweru (mildiou + alternariose</strong>)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikiyitera : uduhumyo Peronospora scheideni + Alternaria porri</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aho ifata : ku mababi no ku bijumba by&rsquo;igitunguru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibimenyetso : Onyo zikiri nto zihinduka umuhondo kandi zikarandurwa n&rsquo;ubusa. Ku bitunguru haba hatwikiriwe n&rsquo;utwoya tweruruka ndetse rimwe na rimwe hakabaho utuntu tw&rsquo;umukara</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uko bayirwanya :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; gusimburanya ibihingwa mu murima</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; guhumbika no gutera onyo mu murima uhinze neza</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; gukoresha imiti ya kizungu :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Dithane : gr 50/L 10 z&rsquo;amazi/ari 2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Cupro-antracol : 2 Kg/ha</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Milraz : 2 Kg/ha</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"100\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-roman\" type=\"i\">\r\no<li><strong>Ububore bw&rsquo;ikijuju : </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikiyitera : uduhumyo (Aspergillus niger na Sclerotium cepivorum)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aho ifata : ibitunguru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibimenyetso : mu gihe bibitse, ibitunguru byuzuraho amoya y&rsquo;ikijuju cyangwa ibintu by&rsquo;umukara kandi bikomeye. Amaherezo ibitunguru birabora neza neza</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uko bayirwanya :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; kwanika neza ibitunguru mbere yo kubihunika kandi bigahunikwa ahantu humutse</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; gukuramo ibitunguru byafashwe kugirango bitanduza ibindi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; kubibika ahantu hari umwuka uhagije kandi bimanitse</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"500\" style=\"list-style-type:lower-roman\" type=\"i\">\r\no<li><strong>Indwara iterwa n&rsquo;inzoka y&rsquo;ibimera : </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikiyitera : inzoka yitwa Angilile (Ditylenchus dispaci)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aho ifata : amababi, ibitunguru</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibimenyetso : onyo ziranuka. Amababi aratumba. Ibitunguru birafobagana. Igitunguru kirisatura maze kikabora.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uko bayirwanya :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; gutwikira mu mwobo onyo zafashwe</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; gusubiza onyo muri uwo murima nyuma y&rsquo;imyaka 4-5</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"10\">\r\no<li><strong>Iminsi zerera</strong> : basarura onyo iyo ibibabi byazo byumye neza neza, igishishwa cy&rsquo;inyuma kimeze nk&rsquo;urupapuro rushaje. Bitewe n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo;ubutunguru n&rsquo;akarere bihinzemo, ibitunguru byera nyuma y&rsquo;amezi 3-4 bigemuriwe mu murima</li>\r\no<li><strong>Umurumbuko :</strong> umusaruro w&rsquo;ibitunguru kuri ha 1 uri hagati ya toni 30 na toni 70 bitewe n&rsquo;uburemere bwa buri gitunguru.</li>\r\no<li><strong>Guhunika :</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; iyo bamaze gusarura onyo zeze, bazanika ku zuba</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; izimaze kugabanukamo amazi bareba izitarwaye, izidatemye bakazibika ku mbaho cyangwa ku byatsi byumye ahantu humutse kandi hinjiramo umwuka uhagije</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; bashobora no kumanika ibitunguru byiza mu gisenge</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>N.B. :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Ibitunguru bishobora kubikwa mu gihe kiri hagati y&rsquo;amezi 4 na 6. Ibyo aribyo byose ibigomba gupfa muri icyo gihe ntibigomba kurenga 30% y&rsquo;ibyabitswe.</li>\r\no<li>Iyi nyandiko ushobora kuyihuza n&rsquo;igihe bitewe n&rsquo;ubushakashatsi bugenda bugerwaho mu buhinzi bw&rsquo;ibitunguru bityo imibare imwe nimwe ikagenda ihinduka bitewe n&rsquo;aho uri kubihinga.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Byateguwe hifashishijwe imfashanyigisha za MINAGRI, 2007</em></p>\r\n",
