        "title": "Ibireti : Ifishi tekiniki yo guhinga kijyambere",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "ibireti.jpg",
        "text": "<p><strong>Ibireti : Ifishi tekiniki yo guhinga kijyambere.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>Aho ibireti bihingwa : bihingwa cyane mu turere tw&rsquo;amakoro.</li>\r\no<li>Ubutaka : igihingwa gikunda ubutaka buhitisha amazi kandi budacuramye cyane.</li>\r\no<li>Amoko yamamazwa : hari Nyiragahini, Capita chef, Kinigi, Bonde, Susa na HAT 1-8.</li>\r\no<li>Gutegura umurima Umurima uhingwamo ibireti ugomba kuba wararwanyijweho isuri kandi uhinze&nbsp;neza.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\no<li>Gufumbira :</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Bashyiraho toni 12 z&rsquo;ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera iboze neza mbere yo gutera.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"6\">\r\no<li>Igerambuto</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Umuhinzi akoresha ibishibu ariko n&rsquo;ingemwe zateguriwe muri pepiniyeri ashobora kuzikoresha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Atera kuri cm 60 kuri cm 80 mu mayogi ashashe ku mirongo ine itandukanyijwe na m 1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Igihe cyitera: ni Werurwe na Gicurasi.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\no<li>Gufata neza ibireti mu mirima</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Imirimo y&rsquo;ingenzi igomba gukorwa:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>gusimbura ingemwe zitafashe, kubagara,</li>\r\no<li>gusasira no gukata</li>\r\no<li>Kurwanya indwara n&rsquo;ibyonnyi hakoreshejwe amoko yihanganira indwara no gutera imiti.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"8\">\r\no<li>Ibyonnyi n&rsquo;indwara by&rsquo;ingenzi byangiza Ibireti</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibyonnyi:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>a) Utuyoka duto tw&rsquo;ibireti: utwo tuyoka batwita Meloidogyne spp. Tugira mm 1</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>kugeza kuri mm 2 kandi tuba mu butaka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibimenyetso</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyo utwo dukoko tumaze kwinjira mu mizi, imizi irabyimba cyangwa hakaza</p>\r\n\r\n<p>uduheri. Iyo bikabije imizi ihagarara gukura bityo igihingwa kikagwingira.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uburyo bwo karwanya no kugakumira:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu kurwanya izo nzoka, umuhinzi atera imbuto nzima no kubisikanya ibihingwa cyane cyane akoresha ibinyampeke (ibigori, ingano,).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Indwara</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>b) Ramulariyoze: iyo ndwara ifata indabyo n&rsquo;amababi iterwa n&rsquo;agahumyo bita Ramularia bellunensis.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikimenyetso: Iyo ndwara igaragazwa n&rsquo;uko indabyo zibora.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uko barwanya iyo indwara: umuhinzi atera amoko y&rsquo;ibireti yihanganira iyo ndwara, guhinga neza bagirira isuku igihingwa, kubisikanya ibireti n&rsquo;ikindi gihingwa (ibirayi); gutera ingemwe neza ahantu h&rsquo;ubutaka buhitisha amazi.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"9\">\r\no<li>Igihe byerera:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Batangira gusarura nyuma y&rsquo;amezi atatu bateye ibishibu.</li>\r\no<li>Mu Rwanda ni itegeko gutera bundi bushya buri mwaka.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"10\">\r\no<li>Gusarura no guhunika:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Nkuko byavuzwe haruguru, batangira gusarura nyuma y&rsquo;amezi 3 bateye ibishibu.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Umusaruro munini uboneka ni toni 3,5 z&rsquo;indabyo mbisi kuri Ha. Nyuma y&rsquo;amezi ya 6, bagakomeza gusarura no mu mezi 6 akurikira.</li>\r\no<li>Iyo indabyo zimaze kuma, bazibika ahantu humutse kandi hagerwa n&rsquo;umwuka uhagije</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
