        "id": 210,
        "title": "Amashaza aribwa imiteja: tumenye uko ahingwa akanitabwaho kijyambere",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "Amashaza aribwa imiteja .png",
        "text": "<p><strong>Uyu Munsi Twige Guhinga amashaza Aribwa Imiteja</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko Igihingwa Cy&rsquo;amashaza Aribwa Imiteja Giteye</strong><br />\r\nUbwoko bw&rsquo;amashaza buribwa imiteja ni ubwoko bwera nk&rsquo;amashaza asanzwe, ariko bukagira umwihariko bukurikije aho bwihanganira kuba, kandi aya mashaza aribwa imiteja ni manini ukurikije ubundi bwoko. Usanga intete z&rsquo;ayo mashaza ari ntoya cyane.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aho Akunda</strong><br />\r\nUbu bwoko bw&rsquo;amashaza bukunda ahantu h&rsquo;imisozi miremire. Arangwa n&rsquo;ibi bikurikira :<br />\r\nubutumburuke buri hagati ya 1500 &ndash; 2600 m<br />\r\nImvura igwa kugeza kuri 1500 mm &ndash; 2100 mm ku mwaka<br />\r\nUbushyuhe buri hagati ya 12&deg;C &ndash; 25&deg;C</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ubutaka</strong><br />\r\nAmashaza y&rsquo;ubwoko bwa snow peas akunda ubutaka butarimo amazi menshi kandi bukize ku ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera; bufite n&rsquo;imyunyu ngugu ya ngombwa.ubwo butaka bugomba kuba bufite ubusharire (pH) buri hagati ya 5 na 7.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gutera Umurima</strong><br />\r\nUmurima uzahingwamo ubu bwoko bw&rsquo;amashaza (snow peas) ugomba kuba utunganyijwe neza nta rwiri rurimo, uhinze neza kugeza nibura mu bujyakuzimu bwa 30 cm; kandi ibyo bigakorwa mbere gato y&rsquo;igihe cy&rsquo;imvura.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Igihe Cy&rsquo;itera</strong><br />\r\nUbu bwoko bw&rsquo;amashaza buterwa igihe imvura itangiye kugwa ariko bitabujije ko abafite amazi n&rsquo;uburyo bwo kuhira batera igihe bashakiye. (Imbuto zihita ziterwa nta kindi bisabye).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uburyo Bukoreshwa Mu Gutera</strong><br />\r\nAmashaza aribwa imiteja (snow peas) aterwa mu buryo bukurikira:<br />\r\n&bull; Haterwa intete imwe nibura mu mwobo ufite ubujyakuzimu buri hagati ya 2.5cm &ndash; 3 cm, 4 cm &ndash; 8 cm hagati y&rsquo;intete n&rsquo;indi<br />\r\n&bull; Umutabo ugomba kuba ufite 70 cm &ndash; 1 m, 50 cm hagati y&rsquo;umurongo n&rsquo;undi</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingano Y&rsquo;imbuto Ikenewe</strong><br />\r\nMu murima ungana na hegitari imwe (1ha) haterwa imbuto ingana n&rsquo;ibiro 50 kg &ndash; 60 cm by&rsquo;imbuto.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ifumbire</strong><br />\r\nAmashaza (snow peas) akenera ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera iboze neza ingana na toni icumi (10T) kuri hegitare imwe (1ha).<br />\r\nAya mashaza ntakenera Azote nyinshi ugeranyije n&rsquo;ubundi bwoko bw&rsquo;imboga.<br />\r\nIfumbire mvaruganda iterwa mu byiciro bibiri. Icyiciro cya mbere batera imbuto hakoreshwa DAP ingana na kilogarama 250 kuri hegitare imwe (250kg/ha); mu kiciro cya kabiri hakoreshwa CAN ingana n&rsquo;ibiro 200 kuri hegitare imwe (200kg/ha) mugihe imbuto iba imaze kuva mu gitaka nyuma y&rsquo;ukwezi.<br />\r\nIfumbire ivangwa neza n&rsquo;igitaka mu murima ugiye guterwamo imbuto.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kuvomera</strong><br />\r\nMu gihe amashaza (Snow peas) atangira kumera akenera amazi kugira ngo abashe gukura neza. Igihe imbuto ikiri mu butaka ikenera kubona amazi nibura kabiri mu munsi mu gitondo izuba ritarava na ni mugoroba izuba rirenze. Iyo igihingwa kimaze gukura wirinda gukoresha amazi menshi kuko bitera indwara mu mizi.<br />\r\nUbundi umumero uboneka hagati y&rsquo;iminsi 5 kugera ku 9 ariko biterwa n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo;ubutaka ndetse n&rsquo;ibihe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gukenura Igihingwa</strong><br />\r\nAmashaza akenera kwicirwa bagabanya amababi kugira ngo igihingwa gishobore kugira ubuhumekero, ibyo bituma kandi kidafatwa n&rsquo;indwara ndetse n&rsquo;udusimba.Gukenura igihingwa bituma kandi kibona urumuri rw&rsquo;izuba bigatuma igihingwa gikoresha neza imirasire y&rsquo;izuba kigakura neza; bituma n&rsquo;imirimo y&rsquo;isarura ikorwa neza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Iminsi Amashaza Yerera</strong><br />\r\nNyuma y&rsquo;ibyumweru bitatu amashaza ahinzwe atangira kurandaranda ku butaka; icyo gihe akenera icyo yuriraho kugira ngo ashobore gukura neza.<br />\r\nAmashaza aribwa imiteja akenera imishingiriro (ni ukuvuga ibiti byumye neza bifite hagati ya 1.5 m &ndash; 2.5 m z&rsquo;uburebure kandi bifite umubyimba wa 3 cm &ndash; 4 cm).<br />\r\nUmushingiro ugomba gutabwa mu butaka kugeza kuri 30 cm.<br />\r\nHagati y&rsquo;umushingiriro n&rsquo;undi haba metero 2 kugeza kuri 2.5m bitewe n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo;amashaza (snow peas).<br />\r\nAmashaza agenda azamukira hagati muri iyi mishingiriro uvuye ku butaka kuri cm 7 kugeza kuri cm 10 hakoreshejwe imigozi iba iziritse ku mishingiriro, amashaza akuriramo hagati. Kirazira ko arandaranda ku butaka kuko ahita aterwa n&rsquo;iindwara ndetse n&rsquo;udusimba bityo bigatuma ataba meza.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Iminsi Amashaza Asarurirwa</strong><br />\r\nUbu bwoko bw&rsquo;amashaza bwera nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi 60 kugeza kuri 70 ni ukuvuga ko isarura rihita ritangira nyuma y&rsquo;iyo minsi rikamara hafi amezi abiri (2)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Umurumbuko</strong><br />\r\nIyo amashaza aribwa imiteja afashwe neza, atanga umusaruro kuva kuri toni 4 kugeza kuri 5 kuri hegitare imwe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko Umusaruro W&rsquo;amashaza Witabwaho</strong><br />\r\nImisogwe y&rsquo;amashaza (Snow peas) ishyirwa ahantu hatava izuba, biba byiza iyo ishyizwe mu gikoresho cya pulasitike, agatwikirwa n&rsquo;umwenda w&rsquo;umweru kugirango bishobore kurengera imisogwe ishobora kwicwa n&rsquo;ubushyuhe.<br />\r\nIbyo umuntu agomba kwitaho mu isarura:<br />\r\nAbasarura bagomba kwisukura intoki mbere yo gusarura kandi bagasukura ibikoresho bakoresha mu isarura.<br />\r\nNtibagomba kuvanga imisogwe n&rsquo;ibindi bintu cyangwa mu bubiko bumwe.<br />\r\nImisogwe ntigomba kuba yanduye; igomba kugirirwa isuku<br />\r\nImisogwe igomba kuba itarwaye; ari icyatsi kibisi, ihehereye (umusogwe ugomba kuba uri hagati ya 1.5 cm &ndash; 2 cm z&rsquo;umubyimba).<br />\r\nImisogwe iri mu rugero rumwe ishyirwa mu gikarito cy&rsquo;ibiro biri hagati ya bitatu na bitanu.<br />\r\nMu kubika ugomba kurenzaho 5% by&rsquo;ibiro wapimye kubera ko umusaruro utakaza uburemere mu gihe cyo kuwutwara.<br />\r\nImisogwe kandi ishobora no kubikwa mu bintu bya pulasitike bifite uburemere bwa 250,500 &ndash; 1000 gm.<br />\r\nIyo umusaruro ujyanwa ku masoko mpuzamahanga inyuma ku makarito urimo handikwaho aho uwo musaruro uturutse.<br />\r\nAho iyo misogwe ibikwa hagomba kuba hatunganyijwe neza hatarengeje ubushyuhe buri hagati ya 0 &ndash; 20&deg;C</p>\r\n",
