        "id": 212,
        "title": "Ibishyimbo bishingirirwa: uko bihingwa kijyambere, uko byitabwaho ngo bitange umusaruro mwiza",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "ibishyimbo bishingirirwa.png",
        "text": "<p><strong>Ibishyimbo bishingirirwa: uko bihingwa kijyambere</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Akamaro k`ibishyimbo bishingirirwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibishyimbo bishingirirwa bigira umusaruro mwinshi ugereranyije n`ibigufi kuko ushobora kwikuba inshuro 3 kugeza kuri 4. Bitanga amafaranga menshi kubera umusaruro mwinshi ndetse no gukundwa ku isoko,Ibishyimbo bigira intungamubiri nyinshi (Ibyubaka umubiri) zijya<br />\r\nkwegera iziri mu nyama, n&rsquo;umunyu ngugu wa feri (Fe). Guhinga ibishyimbo byongera umunyu ntungabihingwa wa Azote mu butaka</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amwe mu moko Y&rsquo;Ibishyimbo bishingirirwa ari mu Rwanda</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibiberanye n`imisozi miremire<br />\r\nGikundiro1 (Mac44) Mpanguhe (RWV3317) Vuzimpundu (RWV 3316)<br />\r\nGirubuzima (RWV 2887) Rukundo (RWV2361) Nyiramata(CAB 2) MAC 42 Gikundiro 3(MAC 9) MAC 28<br />\r\n<strong>Ibishyimbo bishingirirwa bihingwa ryari mu Rwanda?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibishyimbo bishingirirwa biterwa<br />\r\n&bull; Ku Muhindo : Nzeri-Ukwakira (Igihembwe cya A),<br />\r\n&bull; Mu Itumba : Gashyantare-Werurwe (Igihembwe cya B)<br />\r\n&bull; Mu Mpeshyi mu bishanga:Gicurasi-Kamena (Igihembwe cya C).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu bihembwe bibiri bya mbere (urugaryi), ibishyimbo biterwa imvura imaze gusomya ubutaka neza.<br />\r\n<strong>Icyitonderwa :</strong> Guhinga kare, ugatera kare byongera amahirwe yo kweza neza kandi byinshi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gutegura imbuto</strong><br />\r\nUmuhinzi yitegura imbuto y&rsquo;indobanure ingana n&rsquo;ibilo biri hagati ya 40 na 60 kuri hegitari bitewe n&rsquo;ubunini bw&rsquo;ibishyimbo: ibilo 40 ku ntete ntoya, ibilo 60 ku ntete nini,<br />\r\nImbuto nziza y&rsquo;indobanure umuhinzi ashobora kuyivana:<br />\r\n&bull; Muri RAB, cyangwa<br />\r\n&bull; ku mutubuzi w&rsquo;ibishyimbo wemewe na RAB cyangwa<br />\r\n&bull; ku mucuruzi w&rsquo;inyongeramusaruro wemewe.<br />\r\n<strong>Gutegura umurima n&rsquo;ifumbire</strong><br />\r\nGutegura umurima : gusekera imbere y&rsquo;ibyumweru 2 imvura itaragwa no gusanza neza mu gihe cy`itera.<br />\r\nIfumbire: ku murima ufite intambwe 10 ku 10 (ari1) bakoresha ifumbire y`imborera iboze neza ingana n&rsquo;ibitebo 20 (Ibilo 200) n`ifumbire ya DAP ingana na kimwe cya 2 cy&rsquo;ikilo (1/2 kg).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Icyitonderwa :Iyo utabonye DAP ushobora gukoresha NPK 17-17-17 ibilo<br />\r\n2 cyangwa 3 kuri ari 1.<br />\r\nIyo umuhinzi agiye guhinga ibishyimbo mu murima ufite ubusharire ashyiramo ishwagara ingana na toni 5 kuri hegitare cyangwa ibilo 50 kuri ari.<br />\r\n<strong>Gutegura imishingirizo</strong><br />\r\nUmuhinzi ategura imishingirizo 500 ku murima w&rsquo;Intambwe 10 ku 10 (Ari 1) cyangwa imishingirizo 50,000 kuri hegitari (m100 X m100).<br />\r\nImishingirizo igomba kugira nibura uburebure bwa metero 2.5 (m2,5), Imishinigirizo ituruka ku rubingo, inturusu, imigano, no ku biti bivangwa n`imyaka nka gereveriya, kaliyandara, lesena,</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gutera ibishyimbo</strong><br />\r\nIbishyimbo biterwa imvura imaze gusomya ubutaka neza. Biterwa kuri cm 50 (intambwe ebyiri n`igice z`ikiganza) hagati y` umurongo n`undi na cm 20 (intambwe imwe y`ikiganza) hagati y`utwobo tubiri. Utera intete 2 muri buri kobo ku bujyakuzimu bwa cm 5. Ni ngombwa gutera kumurongo</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kubagara no gusukira</strong><br />\r\nIbishyimbo bitangira kubagarwa bwa mbere bimaze ibyumweru 3 kugera kuri 4 bitewe. Gusukira/ kuhira bihita bikorwa nyuma yo kubagara. Iki gikorwa gifasha ibishyimbo kwihanganira indwara z`imizi. Bifasha kandi imishingirizo gukomera.<br />\r\n<strong>Icyitonderwa</strong><br />\r\nNi ngombwa kubagara bwa kabiri n&rsquo;ikindi gihe cyose bibaye ngombwa kuko bifasha ibishyimbo kwera neza</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GUSHINGIRIRA</strong><br />\r\nGushingirira bihita bikorwa nyuma yo kubagara no gusukira/kuhira, mbere y`uko ibishyimbo bitangira kuzana urugoyi. Ushobora gukoresha ibiti bisanzwe cyangwa se uruzitiro rw&rsquo;ibiti ruvanze n`imigozi.<br />\r\nIcyitonderwa: Mu turere tumwe na tumwe nko mu majyaruguru bashingirira ibishyimbo bakimara gutera.Umushingirizo umwe ujya hagati y`imyobo 2 ugafata ibishyimbo 4.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Tubikesha Imfashanyigisho za nozubuhinzi/Minagri</em></p>\r\n",
