        "id": 213,
        "title": "Kabore: Indwara y'ububore bw' imyumbati ",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "imyumbati kabore.png",
        "text": "<p>Izina ry&rsquo;umwimerere :<em>Cassava Brown Streak Virus</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kumenya imiterere y&rsquo;ikibazo </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Indwara ya Kabore uyibwirwa n&rsquo;amabara y&rsquo;umuhondo atangirira ku dutsi tw&rsquo; amababi ariko ntabwo amababi yikunjakuja (apfunyarara), amabara y&rsquo; ikigina agaragara kandi ku giti no kunkondo y&rsquo;ikibabi, ububore bukomeye bufite ibara ry&rsquo;ikigina bugaragara ku bijumba by&rsquo;umwumbati iyo biciwemo ibice. Iyo Kabore ifite ubukana bukabije, umwumbati wose urabora ukicamo ubuniga bwinshi, bigatuma uhindura imiterere. Ubukana bw&rsquo; indwara ya Kabore bugenda bwiyongera kugeza ubwo umusaruro w&rsquo;imyumbati udashobora kuribwa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Igitera indwara ya Kabore n&rsquo;uburyo ikwirakwira Indwara ya Kabore iterwa na virusi iba mu mababi, mu gihimba ndetse no ku gice k&rsquo;umwumbati kiribwa. Kabore ikwirakwizwa n&rsquo; ingeri zo gutera zakuwe ku giti cy&rsquo; umwumbati urwaye. Udusazi duto tw&rsquo; umweru natwo tugira uruhare runini mugukwirakwiza indwara ya Kabore, iyo udusazi tw&rsquo; umweru turumye ku mababi y&rsquo; igiti cy&rsquo; umwumbati kirwaye, tuvanamo virusi itera Kabore tukayikwirakwiza ku myumbati itarwaye igihe tuyirumyeho. Guhererekanya imbuto z&rsquo;imyumbati zirwaye ziva mu karere zijyanwa mu kandi bituma indwara ya Kabore ikwirakwizwa mu bice byinshi bihingwamo imyumbati.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;Inama zigirwa abahinzi </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Gutera ingeri ziturutse ku giti cy&rsquo; imyumbati kitagaragaraho ibimenyetso bya kabore kuko ingeri zitarwaye zimera neza kandi zigakura vuba kuruta izitewe zirwaye.</li>\r\no<li>Kurandura no gutwika cyangwa gutabika ibiti byose byafashwe n&rsquo;uburwayi bwa kabore muri buri murima yagaragayemo.</li>\r\no<li>Kwirinda guhererekanya imbuto z&rsquo;imyubati zivanwa mu karere zijyanwa mu kandi cyane cyane kwirinda kuzivana mu bihugu duturanye aho kabore yabaye icyorezo.</li>\r\no<li>Gusarura hakiri kare bituma igihombo cy&rsquo;umusaruro giterwa na Kabore</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ibi tubikesha ubushakashatsi bwakorewe mu Ikigo cy&rsquo;igihugu gishinzwe guteza imbere ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi na M. Mutumwinka afatanyije J.B. Muhinyuza </em></p>\r\n",
