        "title": "Imyumbati : Igihingwa kiri kw'isonga mu mirire y'abanyarwanda",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "imyumbati foto.jpg",
        "text": "<p>Imyumbati ni igihingwa ni igihingwa gikunda ubutaka buseseka, gihingwa hafi mu Gihugu hose ariko cyane cyane mu ntara y&rsquo;amajyepfo mdetse n&rsquo;iburasirazuba.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu mwaka wa 2014 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe n&rsquo;ikigo cy&rsquo;igihugu cy&rsquo;ibarurirsha mibare ku bufatanye na minisiteri y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;Ubworozi bwagaragaje ko imyumbati ari yo yatanze umusaruro kuruta ibindi bihingwa byose ahoyo n&rsquo;ibindi binyabijumba byihariye 35.9% mu gihembe A ndetse no mu gihembwe B bikiharira 39.2%. Bigaragara kandi ko ubutaka byahizweho ari bwo bunini mu butaka bwahinzwe bwose muri uyu mwaka wa 2014 aho imyumbati yihariye 22.6% by&rsquo;ubutaka byahinzwe bwose mu gihembwe A ndetse no mihembwe ikiharira 23.3% by&rsquo;ubutaka bwahinzwe bwose .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tugiye kureba mu mwaka ushize wa 2015 dusanga imyumbati nanone ikomeje kuza mu myanya ya mbere mu bihingwa bifitiye akamaro abahinzi mu gihugu hose urebye ku musaruro ndetse no ku bwitabire mu kubihinga haba abahinzi bato cyangwa abahinzi bakora ubuhinzi bwagutse . &nbsp;Tugendeye ku butaka byahinzweho mu gihembwe A usanga urutoki (22.9%) rwarahinzwe ahantu hanini kurusha imyumbati (21.5%), ariko nubundi umusaruro w&rsquo;imyumbati n&rsquo;ibinyabijumba &nbsp;ukomeza kuba munini &nbsp;aho ibinyabijumba bifite (31%),mu urutoki rufite &nbsp;(22.5%), naho mu gihembwe B umusaruro w&rsquo;ibinyabijumba wari (33 %), kandi ubuso bwahinzweho imyumbati bukaba ari (22.8%), by&rsquo;ubuso bwahinzwe bwose.Twibanze ku bihembwe A na B kuko mu Gihembwe C ahanini nta myumbati ihingwa ahubwo iki gihembwe kigaragaza umwero w&rsquo;ibirayi mwinshi kurusha ibindi bihingwa .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nubwo ariko imyumbati ifitiye akamaro kanini abahinzi , ikomeje kugaragaza indwara zituma umusaruro ugabanyuka nk&rsquo;uko abahinzi babivuga hirya no hino mu gihugu izo ndwa ariko ubushakashatsi bukaba bugenda bukorwa n&rsquo;ibigo bibishinzwe mugushaka imbuto yahangana nabwo .</p>\r\n",
