        "title": "Ifumbi y'amabere y'inka n'uburyo bwo kuyirinda",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "ifumbiinka.JPG",
        "text": "<p><strong>Andi mazina yayo</strong>: Mammite mu gifarans,&nbsp;Mastitis mu cyongereza</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Indwara y&rsquo;ifumbi y&rsquo;amabere ni iki?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Indwara y&rsquo;ifumbi y&rsquo;amabere ni indwara ifata mu miyoboro y&rsquo;amabere y&rsquo;itungo rikamwa</li>\r\no<li>Iterwa n&rsquo;udukoko two mu bwoko bwa bagiteri(Bacteria), twinjirira mu moko y&rsquo;ibere ririho umwanda cyangwa ririho udusebe, maze twahasanga amata yahasigaye mu gihe cy&rsquo;ikama, tukiyongera buhoro buhoro, tuva mu ibere rimwe tujya mu rindi, kugera dukwiriye icebe ryose</li>\r\no<li>Indwara ibanza kuza mu itungo itagaragaza ibimenyetso (subclinical), ikazagera igihe ibimenyetso bigaragara hanze.</li>\r\no<li>Mu Rwanda, iyi ndwara ihangayikishije aborozi benshi, cyane cyane abakora ubworozi bwa kijyambere.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ifumbi ni indwara mbi kubera izihe mpamvu?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Itera igihombo kinini mu bworozi kubera ko inka irwaye idakamwa neza</li>\r\no<li>Ibere rirwaye ribabaza inka ku buryo itarisha neza</li>\r\no<li>Hariho tumwe mu dukoko dutera ifumbi y&rsquo;amabere dufata abantu n&rsquo;amatungo ku buryo abantu bashobora kwandura.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko yandura</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Muri rusange isuku nke niyo itera ifumbi</li>\r\no<li>Udukoko twinjira mu miyoboro y&rsquo;ibere bitewe ahanini n&rsquo;icebe rifite umwanda</li>\r\no<li>Umukamyi nawe ashobora kwanduza amatungo mu gihe yabanje gukama icebe rirwaye cyangwa afite imyanda ku intoki.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibimenyetso by&rsquo;ifumbi y&rsquo;amabere</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Icebe n&rsquo;ibere birabyimba cyane, bigahinda umuriro, wakoraho inka ikagutera umugeri kubera ububabare;</li>\r\no<li>Itungo rirwaye ntiribasha kurisha</li>\r\no<li>Ahafashwe n&rsquo;uburwayi hashobora kuzamo ibibyimba</li>\r\no<li>Iyo bitinze icebe rishobora kuziba burundu</li>\r\no<li>Amata y&rsquo;inka irwaye ifumbi ahindura ibara, agakunda gucika, akagaragaramo amaraso cyangwa ibibumbe;</li>\r\no<li>Icebe rirwaye riba rikomeye nk&rsquo;ibuye iyo urikanze</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>ifumbi y&rsquo;amabere y&rsquo;inka</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko ifumbi y&rsquo;amabere yirindrwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Ifumbi y&rsquo;amabere ni indwara iboneka kenshi, ariko aborozi bashobora kuyirinda bita ku isuku y&rsquo;inka, iy&rsquo; umukamyi, iy&rsquo;ikiraro n&rsquo;iy&rsquo;ibikoreresho. Babigeraho bita ku isuku y&rsquo;ibintu byose bikora ku mabere y&rsquo;itungo, birinda ibintu byose udukoko tuyitera twakwihishamo</li>\r\no<li>By&rsquo;umwihariko, umworozi agomba kwita kuri ibi bikurikira</li>\r\no<li>kugira isuku mu kiraro ukuka buri munsi uharinda ivumbi cyangwa icyondo;</li>\r\no<li>koza neza ibikoresho byogukama ukabyumutsa neza</li>\r\no<li>gukaraba intoki n&rsquo; isabune, intoki zikumuka mbere yo gukama</li>\r\no<li>koza amabere n&rsquo;utuzi tw&rsquo;akazuyazi mbere yo gukama</li>\r\no<li>guhanagura icebe ukoresheje agatambaro kumutse</li>\r\no<li>inka igaragaza ibimenyetso by&rsquo;ifumbi ikamwa nyuma y&rsquo;izindi kugira ngo umukamyi abe atashobora kwanduza izindi</li>\r\no<li>ibere ry&rsquo;inka rigaragaza ibimenyetso by&rsquo;ifumbi na ryo rikamwa nyuma y&rsquo;amabere mazima kandi ayo mata ntateranywa n&rsquo;ay&rsquo;amabere mazima.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko ifumbi y&rsquo;amabere ivurwa</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>inka irwaye ifumbi ivurwa hakoreshejwe imiti yo mu bwoko bwa antibiotics nka&nbsp;<em>Gentamycin</em>,Amoxycillin, procain-penicillin na dihydrostreptomycin sulfate, <em>streptomycin,</em>&nbsp;Amoxycillin trihydrate na Naomycin sulfate. Ariko ni ngombwa kubanza gusuzumisha muri laburatwari kugira ngo hamenyekane umuti nyawo uhwanye n&rsquo;udukoko turi muri iyo nka.</li>\r\no<li>Mu rwego rwo kwirinda ifumbi umworozi agomba kugira akamenyetso ko gusuzumisha buri gihe inka ze yifashishije laburatwari kugira ngo inka zafashwe zivurwe hakiri kare amabere Atari yaziba.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&nbsp;Byateguwe na Arcade Nshimiyimana (nshimarcade@gmail.com&nbsp;) hifashishije inyigisho z&rsquo;ikigo k&rsquo;igihugu gishinzwe iterambere ry&rsquo;ubuhinzi</em></p>\r\n",
