        "title": "Beterave: Uburyo bwo kuzihingaÂ kijyambere",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "Beterave pi.png",
        "text": "<p><strong>Beterave ni iki?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Beterave ( Izwi ku izina rya: Beta vulgaris L ) ni igihingwa kiri mu muryango w&rsquo;ibinyabijumba icyo gice twakwita ikijumba akaba ari nacyo kiribwa .Nkuko tubikesha abakoze ubushakashatsi kuri icyo gihingwa batubwira ko gikomoka mugice cya mediterane . Beterave ikungahaye ku myunyu ya feri(Fer) na fosipore (Phosphore). Ikindi twavuga kuri ikigihingwa ni uko atari ngombwa ko uba ufite isambu nini kugira ngo ube wagihinga ,ni ukuvuga abakoresha akarima k&rsquo;igikoni nabo bashobora guhinga Beterave .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aho wakorera ubuhinzi bwa Betera&nbsp; ve:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Beterave ikunda ikirere kidashyuha ,ariko nkuko bizwi ku binyabijumba ikigihingwa gisaba ubushyuhe buri hagati ya 15- 23 &deg;C kugirango gikure neza .Nibyiza kugishyira ahantu hari ubushyuhe bwa dogere 0-8 &deg;C igihe kiri kumera . Beterave yihanganira ubushyuhe tuyigereranije na caroti , gikunda ubutaka burimo umusenyi (sol sablo-limoneux ou sableux) . Beterave yihanganira ubusharire bw&rsquo;ubutaka butarengeje 6 .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko bahinga Beterave :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amwe mumoko akunze guhingwa twavugamo Ruby queen, Red Ace F1 na Pacemaker III F1. Hahingwa imbuto za Beterave bitandukanye na bimwe mubihingwa ushobora gutera ingeri za byo nk&rsquo; ibijumba imyumbati&hellip;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Itubuto turi hagati ya 30 na 50 nitwo dusanga muri garama y&rsquo;umurama wa Beterave .<br />\r\nIhingwa rya Beterave rikorerwa bwambere muri pepiniyeri usiga intera ya santimetero 5 (5 cm) hagati y&rsquo;imirongo na 5 cm hagati y&rsquo;akabuto n&rsquo;akandi .<br />\r\nUkoresha garama ziri hagati ya 25- 30 g z&rsquo;umurama k&rsquo;ubuso bwa metero kare m2. Ni byiza gushyira mumazi y&rsquo;akazuyazi mugihe cy&rsquo;amasaha 5 kugera kuri 6 mbere yo guhinga.<br />\r\nBeterave ikurwa muri pepiniyeri ishyirwa mu murima wateguwe imaze kugira amababi 4 kugera kuri 5,kugirango utangire kubona umusaruro utegereza amezi 4 kugera kuri 5.<br />\r\nUshobora guhinga Beterave utabanje kuzinyuza mu buhumbikiro icyo gihe ufata ibiro 10- 15 kg by&rsquo;umurama kuri hegitari.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibyonnyi n&rsquo;uko wabirwanya :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nibyiza gufata ingamba zikomeye kugirango ugabanye ikoreshwa ry&rsquo;imiti iva mungana kuko yangiza ibidukikije hakoreshwa isimburanya ry&rsquo;ibihingwa n&rsquo;ibindi.. (rotation culturale, lutte int&eacute;gr&eacute;e, d&eacute;sherbage, etc&hellip;). Imiti ikinze gukoreshwa twavuga : Malathion na Carbaryl irwanya udutagangurirwa &hellip;, Pyllerin irwanya inyo</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gusarura :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nyuma y&rsquo;amezi agera kuri 4 ,ushobora gutangira kubona umusaruro . Iyo Beterave imaze kugera igihe cy&rsquo;isarura Ukata ibibabi ukoresheje ibikoresho bya bugenewe ukirinda gukomeretsa ikijumba, niyo mpamvu byakabaye byiza ubanje koroshya ubutaka kugirango gusarura bize koroha hatabaye ho kwangiza ibijumba. Iyo umaze kurandura beterave ukata ibice cyo hejuru kigizwe n&rsquo;ibibabi ukabisiga mumurima kugirango bibe ifumbire .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Icyitonderwa : Izi ngero zigenda zivugwa hano zishobora guhinduka bitwe n&rsquo;inama z&rsquo;ushinzwe ubuhinzi ashingiye ku miterere y&rsquo;ubutaka bwawe.</p>\r\n",
