        "id": 230,
        "title": "Tumenye Guhinga Butternut squash (Cucurbita moschata) ubwoko bw'ibihaza/imyungu",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "Batternut quash imyungu .png",
        "text": "<ol>\r\no<li><strong>Butternut squash (Cucurbita moschata) ni gihingwa ki?</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Iki ni igihingwa kiri mu bwoko bw&rsquo;ibihaza cyangwa imyungu gihingwa kw&rsquo;isi yose. Ni igihingwa gitinya ubukonje kandi kigakunda ahantu hafite ubushyuhe butari bwinshi cyane. Ibihaza byacyo biba n&rsquo;ibara ry&rsquo;umuhondo werurutse naho imbere mu gihaza hakaba hasa na Oranje (orange) iri bara rikaba rigaragaza ko iki gihingwa gikize muri Vitamin A ariko kikaba cyifitemo na Potasium, Vitamini C na Manganese. Iki gihingwa kigira imbuto zisa zose zipima gm 650-1000. Ugereranije n&rsquo;ibindi bihanza n&rsquo;indi myungu iki gihingwa ni kiza kuko cyera vuba kubirusha byose, Iki gihingwa ntabwo kiribwa kidatetse naho kugiteka byo bikorwa mu buryo butandukanye ariko habanje gukurwamo imbuto.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\no<li><strong>Ibyo gikenera </strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibijyanye n&rsquo;ubushyuhe:</strong>Ibipimo by&rsquo;ubushyuhe busabwa ngo iki gihingwa kimere neza (Germination) :20-25<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">o</span></sup>C.Ubushyuhe bukenerwa mu mikurire isanzwe: 18-25<sup><span style=\"font-size:small\">o</span></sup>C. Iki gihingwa ntago cyihanganira ikigero cy&rsquo;ubukonje kiri hasi kuko ubukonje bwangiza ibihingwa bikiri bito ndetse nibyenda gusaza. Iki gihingwa rero kigomba guhingwa ahantu hatari ubukonje bukabije mu gihe cy&rsquo;imikurire yacyo</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ubutaka:</strong>pH:6.0-6.5, Umusaruro mwiza uboneka mu butaka buseseka kandi buhirisha amazi bukaba bufite umunyu mucye ndetse bufite imborera ihagije</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gutegura ubutaka:</strong>Ubutaka bugomba gutegurwa mbere yo gutera imbuto. Ibisigazwa by&rsquo;ibihingwa byahinzwe mbere bigomba kubanza bikarandurwa neza mu murima bigashiramo. Niba aho ugiye guhinga hagwa imvura nyinshi ugomba gukora kuburyo mumurima wawe hatazarekamo amazi ,ugakora ibimeze nk&rsquo;amayogi manini mu murima kugirango amazi atazareka bikangiza ibihingwa byawe.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\no<li><strong>Gutera n&rsquo;amabwiriza yabyo</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Butternuts nyinshi ziterwa ku buryo bwo gutera imbuto mu butaka hatabanje kubaho guhumbika cyangwa kwinaza. Ariko abahinzi bamwe bahitamo no guhumbika mbere y&rsquo;uko igihe cy&rsquo;itera kigera kugirango bazabone umusaruro mbere y&rsquo;uko byabindi byatewe bitari byera . Ibi bifasha kugirango umuhinzi abone umusaruro ashobora kuba ajyana kw&rsquo;isoko mbere y&rsquo;uko ibyo yahinze byera. Aha uburyo bwo kugemura bikorwa mbere y&rsquo;uko igihingwa kizana imizi byinshi aho cyahumbitswe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Intera mu gutera:</strong>Aha bigenda bihinduka ariko uko byagenda kose hagomba kuba ibihingwa 14,000-18,000 kuri hegitari imwe . Hagati y&rsquo;umurongo n&rsquo;undi hajya m1,5 hanyuma hagati y&rsquo;igihingwa n&rsquo;ikindi hakajya cm40.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ifumbire:</strong>Kugirango hakoreshwe ifumbire neza umuhinzi ubishoboye abanza gupima ubutaka bwe. Butternuts kimwe n&rsquo;ubundi bwoko bw&rsquo;ibihaza byishimira cyane ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera ariko bikanakenera n&rsquo;ifumbire mvaruganda yo kunganira iyo mborera kugirango umusaruro wiyongere. Uko ugenda ukoresha ifumbire y&rsquo;imborera imyaka nyinshi niko ubutaka buzarushaho kudakenera ifumbire mvaruganda.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amabwiriza mugushyiramo ifumbire</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>N-ibiro 130. 50% mbere yo guhinga iyindi isigaye igashyirwamo mu byiciro bitatu bikurikirana usigamo intera y&rsquo;ibyumeru bitatu .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>P-ibiro 50kg Byose bishyirwa mu murima mbere yo gutera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>K-ibiro 150 , 30% mbere yo gutera,30% nyuma y&rsquo;ibyumweru bine uteye,30% mu kuzana uruyange rwa mbere,10% mu gihe imbuto za mbere zagaragaye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ibi ni ibijyanye n&rsquo;ibikenerwa n&rsquo;igihingwa ariko bitewe n&rsquo;uburyo ubutaka bumeze hakorwa gusanisha ubutaka nibyo bukeneye ngo igihingwa gitange umusaruro cyitezweho.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kuhira:</strong>Butternuts zishobora guhindwa ku butaka butagira imvura cg bugira imvura nke ariko hagakorwa kuhira kugirango haboneke umusaruro wifuzwa. Amazi azakenerwa azaterwa n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo;ubutaka, igihe igihingwa gihingiwe ndetse n&rsquo;uko igihingwa kigenda gikura. Hagomba kwirindwa ko hakoreshwa amazi arenze urugero rugenwe kandi hakirindwa ko haba ibidendezi mu murima . Amazi akenewe ubusanzwe ni mm 25-45 mu cyumweru ku gihingwa . Aha ni byiza gukoresha uburyo bwo kuhira bugeza amazi ku gihingwa mu buryo bwa &ldquo;Drip irrigation&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibindi by&rsquo;ingenzi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>Kurandura ibyatsi bidakenewe mu murima bikoreshwa intoki kandi mu gihe igihingwa kikiri gito.</li>\r\no<li>Umuyaga mwinshi ushobora kwangiza ibihingwa , aho bishoboka hashyirwaho uruzitiro rwo kuwurinda.</li>\r\no<li>Iminsi bisaba ngo igihingwa cyimere: 5-10</li>\r\no<li>Iminsi isabwa ngo usarure: 90-100</li>\r\no<li>Urumuri rukenerwa:Urumuri rw&rsquo;izuba ruhagije</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\no<li><strong>Gusarura no kujyana kw&rsquo;isoko</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Hokoreshwa icyuma cyangwa umukasi wabugenewe mu gukata igihaza ku gihingwa hirindwa kwangiza inkondo isigara ku gihingwa ndetse n&rsquo;isigara ku gihaza. Mu kujyana kw&rsquo;isoko ushahora gufunga ibihaza mu dufuka tw&rsquo;ibiro 10,7,5 cyangwa 3 bitewe n&rsquo;ubwoko bw&rsquo;abakiriya ufite. Gusarura bikoreshwa ibitebo cyangwa ibikarito byabugenewe. Butternuts zisaruwe mu gihe cy&rsquo;imvura zishobora kuba zanduye cg zifite ibyondo zishobora kubanza zikozwa hagategezwa ko zumuka neza kugirango zipakirwe zijyanwa kw&rsquo;isoko. Butternuts kandi zishobora kubikwa igihe gito mbere y&rsquo;uko zijyanwa kw&rsquo;isoko ariko ukazibika wizeyeko zifite isuku ihagije , ahantu humutse neza kandi muri zo hakaba ntayangiritse irimo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Icyitonderwa : Ahakoreshejwe ijambo Butternuts bishatse kuvuga <strong>Butternut squash (</strong>Cucurbita moschata<strong>)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Byateguwe na <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/etienne-niyigaba\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">NIYIGABA Etienne</span></a> . Hifashishijwe imfashanyigisho za FAO na STARKE AYRES</em></p>\r\n",
