        "id": 231,
        "title": "Urutoki: indwara n'ibyonnyi n'uburyo birwanywa",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "urutoki insina.png",
        "text": "<p>Mu nkuru zacu ziheruka twabagejejeho <a href=\"https://yeanrwanda.org/2015/04/23/urutoki-uyu-munsi-menya-uko-baruhinga/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#1ab106\">uburyo bwo guhinga Urutoki kuburyo bwa kijyambere</span></a>. Aha rero twabashakiye uburyo bwo kurinda urutoki rwawe ntiruhungabanywe n&rsquo;indwara ndetse n&rsquo;ibyonnyi nk&rsquo;uko tubikesha Minisiteri y&rsquo;ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi mw&rsquo;ishami ryayo rishinwe isakazamakuru.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Indwara z&rsquo;ingenzi n&rsquo;uburyo bwo Kuzirwanya</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:decimal\" type=\"1\">\r\no<li><strong>Indwara ya Fizariyoze</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyi ndwara iterwa n&rsquo;agahumyo bita <em>Fusarium oxysporium f. sp. cubense</em>; insinayafashwe amakoma agenda ahinduka umuhondo uhereye kuyo hasi. Nyuma y&rsquo;iminsi mike amakoma aruma maze agatendera ku mutumba, umwumba nawo uhita wuma. Iyo utemye umutumba usangamo ububore bugaragazwa n&rsquo;amabara y&rsquo;ikigina n&rsquo;ayirabura. Iyi ndwara yibasira cyane ubwoko bw&rsquo;insina za Kayinja, Gros michel, Kamaramasenge n&rsquo;izindi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Guyikumira no kuyirwanya</strong> : kurandura no gutaba insina zose zafashwe, zigasimbuzwa ubwoko bwihangana (nibura nyuma y&rsquo;umwaka) nk&rsquo;intuntu, intokatoki, inyamunyu, n&rsquo;izindi cyangwa indi myaka; kudatera insina zirwaye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Icyitonderwa</strong>: Iyi ndwara ishobora kumara igihe kirekire mu butaka.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:decimal\" type=\"1\">\r\no<li><strong>Kirabiranya y&rsquo;urutoki</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyi ndwara<strong> </strong>iterwa na Bagiteri bita <em>Banana Xanthomonas Campestris</em>. Indwara ya kirabiranya (bagiteriyoze) iterwa n&rsquo;agakoko ko mu bwoko bwa xanthomonas. Insina yafashwe, amakoma yazo ararabirana, umutumba wayo avamo amashyira y&rsquo;umuhondo, amabere atangira kuneka atarakura; iyo umanyuye ibere, usangamo ibara ry&rsquo;ikigina imbere; umwanana urabora kandi ukwuma. Indwara ikwirakwizwa n&rsquo;inzuki zitara ubuki, imibyare irwaye n&rsquo;ibikoresho bidasukuye.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Uko bayirwanya:</strong> guca imwana ukoresheje isando amabere yanyuma akimara gusohoka mu mwanana; gutera imibyare myiza nk&rsquo;ivuye muri laboratoire; gusukura ibikoresho n&rsquo;umuliro, gutema no gutaba insina zirwaye.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\" style=\"list-style-type:decimal\" type=\"1\">\r\no<li><strong>Karadosiporiyoze</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Iyi ndwara iterwa n&rsquo;agahumyo bita <em>Cladosporium musae</em>; iyi ndwara igaragazwa n&rsquo;amabara maremare y&rsquo;ikigina kivanze n&rsquo;umukara ku makoma. Amakoma yafashwe cyane aruma. Ikunze kugaragara mu gihe cy&rsquo;imvura ivaze n&rsquo;ubuhehere bwinshi. Gukumira no kurwanya: kwirinda gutera insina uzegeranyije; kwicira insina, buri kwezi , umwuka n&rsquo;urumuri bigatemberamo neza; gufumbira urutoki rugahora rutohagiye no gutera ubwoko bukunda kurwanya iyo ndwara</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ibyonnyi n&rsquo;uburyo bwo kubirwanya</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Imungu y&rsquo;insina</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Imungu y&rsquo;insina bita <em>Cosmopolites sordidus</em>, ni agakoko gasa n&rsquo;umukara gafite umunwa muremure ko mu bwoko bw&rsquo;ikivumvuri. Icyana (igishorobwa) ni umweru, umutwe wacyo usa n&rsquo;umuhondo uvanze n&rsquo;ikigina, nta maguru kigira. Nicyo gitobagura imyobo mu nguri. Iyo imyobo imaze kuba myinshi, umuyaga utari mwinshi utuma insina yirindimura hasi. Amakoma y&rsquo;insina yafashwe cyane ahinduka umuhondo agapfunyarara nyuma akuma. Insina zamunzwe, zigaragara neza mu gihe cy&rsquo;impeshyi n&rsquo;igihe zitangiye kwana. Ikunda kandi yororoka neza kandi vuba ahantu hashyuha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gukumira no kurwanya</strong>: gukorera neza urutoki; gutera imibyare ivuye mu rutoki rutarwaye; gutera bundi bushya nyuma y&rsquo;imyaka nibura itatu aharimbuwe izari zafashwe; gutega imungu: batemagura umutumba bamaze gucaho igitoke bakawurekera hasi kugira ngo ukurure imungu. Nyuma bakawukura mu rutoki bakawutwika; kurimbura inguri zishaje no kutongeramo insina mu rutoki igihe rukirimo izafashwe n&rsquo;imungu; gutwikiriza igitaka inguri bamaze gutemaho igitoki kugira ngo imungu ibure aho itera amagi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Iyi nkuru tuyikesha imfashanyigisho za Minisiteri y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;ubworozi.</em></p>\r\n",
