        "id": 247,
        "title": "Uko wamenya ibura ry'intungagihingwa igihingwa gikenera cyane (NPK) muri rusange",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "IMG-20160505-WA0008.jpg",
        "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Uko wamenya ibura ry&rsquo;intungagihingwa igihingwa gikenera cyane (NPK) muri rusange </span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Izo ntungagihingwa ni Azoti (N), Fosifori (P) na Potasiyumu cyangwa Potasi (K) kuko igihingwa kizikenera cyane, zkaba ari nazo zikunda kubura mu butaka kenshi iyo budafumbirwa bigateza ikibazo ku gihingwa ntigitange umusaruro cyari kitezweho. Umuhinzi ni ngombwa ko amenya uko igihingwa kibura izi ntungagihingwa kiba kimeze bitewe n&rsquo;izibura mu butaka maze akabasha kuzongeramo . Twifashishije inyandiko &ldquo;Duhinge Kijyambere, agatabo ka 2&rdquo; yateguwe na Minisiteri y&rsquo;Ubuhinzi n&rsquo;Ubworozi na <span style=\"color:#000000\"> </span>&ldquo; Ibimenyetso biranga ibura ry&rsquo;intungagihingwa&rdquo; cyanditswe na IFDC tubagejejeho iyi nyandiko dushimira <span style=\"color:#000000\"> </span>n&rsquo;abo tuvuze bagize uruhare mu gutegura izi nyandiko zombi.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Azoti (N) </span></strong></span></p>\r\no</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Azoti mu kimera </span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Nubwo Azoti iba mu mwuka wo mu kirere ari nyinshi (79%), ishobora gukoreshwa n&rsquo;ibihingwa gusa iyo ibonetse mu buryo bwa Nitarati (NO3) cyangwa mu buryo bwa Amoniyumu (NH4). Bagiteri za rizobiyumu ziba mu mizi y&rsquo;ibinyamisogwe zishobora guhindura Azoti iba mu mwuka wo mu kirere maze igakoreshwa n&rsquo;igihingwa. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Azoti ni intungagihingwa y&rsquo;ingenzi ikenerwa n`ikimera ku rugero ruri hejuru. Ni intungagihingwa y&rsquo;ingenzi iboneka muri kororofili (itangabara ry&rsquo;icyatsi), mu byubaka umubiri nka poroteyine n&rsquo;ibindi bigize igihingwa. Azoti itanga ibara ry&rsquo;icyatsi kibisi cyijimye ku bihingwa kandi ikongera imikuririre y&rsquo;ibihingwa. Yongera ubwiza bw&rsquo;amababi, imikorere y&rsquo;amafufu aboneka mu biribwa ndetse na poroteyine ziboneka mu ntete z&rsquo;ibihingwa n&rsquo;ubwatsi bw&rsquo;amatungo. Ibimera bigira Azoti iri ku rugero rwa 1 - 5% mu buremere. Azoti irenze ibipimo igihingwa gikeneye ituma igihingwa gitohagira cyane bigatuma gishobora kwibasirwa n&rsquo; ibyonyi n&rsquo; indwara nyinshi. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ibimenyetso bigaragaza ibihingwa bibura Azoti</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Amababi yo hasi ashaje aba umuhondo. </span></span></p>\r\no</li>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Iyo ibura rya azoti rikabije, bigaragazwa n&rsquo;utudomo tuza ku isonga no mu mpande z`ikibabi tugana hagati mu kibabi kandi igihingwa kikagwingira. </span></span></p>\r\no</li>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ibihingwa bidafite azoti ihagije biragwingira, bikarabya kandi bikazana imbuto imburagihe; bisobanura ko igihingwa kizana imbuto kitarakura neza. </span></span></p>\r\no</li>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Ibi bituma umusaruro n&rsquo;ubwiza bwawo bugabanuka.</span></span></p>\r\no</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Fosifori (P) </span></strong></span></p>\r\no</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Fosifori mu bimera</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Fosifori ni intungagihingwa iza ku mwanya wa kabiri nyuma ya Azoti mu ntungagihingwa zikenerwa ku rugero ruri hejuru mu mikurire myiza y&rsquo;ibihingwa. Igira akamaro mu kwiyongera k&rsquo;uturemangingo, no mu mikurire y&rsquo;imbuto. Ituma imizi ya mbere ikura neza, ituma amababi yiyongera, ituma igihingwa kibyara, ituma kirabya n&rsquo;umusaruro w&rsquo;impeke ukaba mwinshi kandi mwiza. Fosifori kandi yihutisha ukwera kw&rsquo;igihingwa. Fosifori ituma imizi yiyongera kandi ikaba miremire bigatuma ivoma neza amazi n&rsquo;intungagihingwa. Ituma kandi igihingwa gifata mu butaka neza bikakirinda kugwa. Urugero rwa Fosifori mu gihingwa ruri hagati ya 0.1-0.4%. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Ibimenyetso biranga ibihingwa bibura Fosofori </strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Ibara ry&rsquo;ubururu, cyangwa umwura (move) cyangwa rijya gutukura n`umuhondo muke ku bibabi byo hasi (ibikuze cyane); imikurire rusange y`igihingwa iradindira (iratinda). </span></p>\r\no</li>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Imizi y&rsquo;igihingwa ikura nabi kandi ikaba migufi. </span></p>\r\no</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>3. Potasiyumu (K) </strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Potasiyumu mu bimera </strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Bitandukanye n&rsquo;izindi ntungagihingwa, Potasiyumu ntifatana n&rsquo;izindi, ahubwo iguma yonyine igafasha igihingwa kuringaniza imisemburo, ikoreshazuba (photosynthesis), gukoresha amazi neza, gukora amido (amafufu) ndetse na poroteyine ku gihingwa. Ibihingwa bigira Potasiyumu ku rugero rumwe na Azoti ariko ibihingwa bitanga umusaruro uri hejuru bikenera Potasiyumu nyishi kurusha Azoti. Ubutaka bwinshi bugira Potasiyumu iri ku rugero rwo hejuru ariko igice gito cyayo nicyo gishobora gukoreshwa n&rsquo;igihingwa. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Ibimenyetso biranga ibihingwa bibura Potasiyumu </strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Kimwe mu bimenyetso biranga ibura rya Potasiyumu mu gihingwa ni: </span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">ugupfunyarara no kubabuka kw&rsquo;impera z&rsquo;amababi y&rsquo;igihingwa. </span></p>\r\no</li>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Kuko Potasiyumu yimuka mu gihingwa, ibura ryayo rigaragarira mbere na mbere ku mababi ashaje. </span></p>\r\no</li>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Ibihingwa bibura Potasiyumu bikura buhoro kandi bikagira imizi mike itameze neza. </span></p>\r\no</li>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Inkondo z&rsquo;amababi zigira imbaraga nke kandi akenshi zikagondama. Intete n&rsquo;imbuto biba bitoya kandi bikumagara; </span></p>\r\no</li>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">ibihingwa ntibibasha kwihanganira indwara n&rsquo;ibura ry&rsquo;amazi. </span></p>\r\no</li>\r\no<li>\r\no<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Ibihingwa bibura Potasiyumu bifatwa n&rsquo;indwara vuba kandi bikagira umusaruro muke w&rsquo;imbuto kandi utari mwiza. </span></p>\r\no</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><em>NIYIGABA Etienne (eniyigaba@yeanrwanda.org)</em></span></p>\r\n",
        "category_id": 3,
        "subcategory_id": 25,
