        "id": 279,
        "title": "Dusobanukirwe n'Indwara ya Rift Valley Fever ifata amatungo n'abantu",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "Rift_Valley_Fever.jpg",
        "text": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>Dusobanukirwe n’Indwara ya Rift Valley Fever ifata amatungo n’abantu</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Indwara ya Rift Valley Fever ni indwara iterwa na Virusi ya Rift Valley Fever Virus ifata amatungo yuza ndetse n’abantu. Iyi virus iba mu muryango wa <em>Bunyaviridae</em> ikaba ari umwihariko muri Afurika yo munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara. Iyi ndwara yakunze kwibasira ibihugu nka Kenya Somaliya, Tanzaniya, Madagasicari, Afurika y’Epfo, Misiri, Sudani n’ibindi .</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>Uko ikwirakwizwa</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyi ndwara ya RVF yagaragaye bwa mbere muri Kenya mu nkengero z’ikiyaga cya Naivasha ahagana mu 1930 ubu ikaba imaze hafi ikinyejana muri Afurika yo munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara. Iyi ndwara yagaragaje ubukana bukomeye mu gihugu cya Misiri mu mwaka wa 1977 ubwo abantu ibihumbi ijana bayanduye abagera kuri 600 bakahasiga ubuzima naho muri Kenya niho yahitanye amatungo menshi mu mwaka wa 1950-1951 aho yahitanye intama zigera ku bihumbi 100. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyi virusi itera RVF ikwirakwizwa n’umubu wo mu bwoko bwa <em>Aedos</em> iba mu bidendezi by’amazi igakwirakwizwa ku buryo bw’amagi y’iyo mibu. Ubundi bwoko bw’imibu nka <em>Culex </em>nayo yihutisha gukwirakwiza iyi ndwara. Imyamaswa zuza (nk’ihene, intama, inka) ndetse n’abantu bashobora kwandura . Amatungo yagaragayemo iyi ndwara araramburura cyane.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Abantu bandura iyi ndwara bitututse mu gukora ku maraso, umubiri w’amatungo yanduye iyi ndwara. Ibi bishobora kuba mu gihe cyo kubaga,</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">kuvura amatungo ndetse no gufasha amatungo kubyara. Abantu bacye bashobora kwanduzwa no kurumwa n’umubu ufite iyo ndwara . Kuba umuntu uyirwaye yayanduza undi ntago biraragara. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Uko ukwirakwizwa guteye gutya: </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Virusi yayo ishobora gukwirakwizwa n’umubu w’ingore binyuze mu magi yawo.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Muri aya magi virusi igumamo imyaka myinshi mu gihe cy’izuba</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Imvura nyinshi ituma amagi afite ya virusi abyara imibu</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyo imibu yiyongereye ubushobozi bwo kwanduza amatungo buriyongera bityo n’uburyo amatungo yanduza abantu bukiyongera</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyo imatungo yanduye ari menshi bituma abaveterineri bayitaho bayavura, bikongera ibyago by’uko indwara ikwirakwira mu bantu.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyi ndwara yakunze kugaragare cyane abantu hane hakurikira: Mu bishanga byereye imigezi, ahantu harangwa no kuba imvura nke, ahantu huhirwa (hahora ibidendezi bituma imibu iba myinshi), no mu misozi miremire ihehereye. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>Ibimenyetso n’uko ivurwa</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Iyi Virusi ya RVF imara iminsi hagati 2-6 mu muntu mbere y’uko igaragaza ibimenyetso. Akenshi abantu bafashwe n’iyi ndwara nta bimenyetso bagaragaza cyangwa bakagaragaza bicye birimo umuriro. Abarwayi bayo bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso baba bafite umuriro, bagacika intege, kubabara mu rutirigongo ndetse no kuzungera. Umurwayi ashobora gukira mu minsi hagati y’2 n’icyumweru kimwe.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Umubare mucye w’abanduye iyi ndwara (8-10%) bagaragaza ibimenyetso bikomeye birimo:</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Kubabara amaso </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Kugira ibibazo mu bwonko bishobra guteza umutwe, Koma, ibi ariko bigaragra gacye ku kigero cya 1% cy’abafashwe n’iyi ndwara bishora kuvamo n’urupfu ariko ku buryo bucye cyane.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Symbol;\">·</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Kuva Imyuna nabyo bigaragara kuri bacye mubafashwe n’iyi ndwara (1%) ariko mubabigaragaje 50% bishobora kubaviramo urupfu.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>Ikigero cyo kwandura iyi ndwara n’ibyo yangiza</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Ugereranyije abantu 1% mu banduye iyi ndwara nibo yica ariko ku matungo uyu mubare uriyongera cyane kuburyo amatungo ahaka yose 100% araramburura. Ku nyigo yakozwe ku bantu byagaragaye ko kuba mu cyaro no kurara hanze ahantu hagaragaye iyi ndwara byongera ibyago byo kurumva n’imibu ikwirakwiza iyi ndwara. Abaveterineri, abakora mu matungo, ababazi, aba bose baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyi ndwara. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><strong>Uko ivurwa</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Kugeza ubu nta muti wihariye kuri iyi ndwara mu bantu urabaho.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\">Mu matungo uburyo bwo gukumira ikwirakwiza ni ukuyakingira. Urukingo rukunze gukoreshwa ni Smithburn ariko hari izndi nkingo ziri gushakashakwa zishobora no gukorehswa ku bantu. </span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);font-size: medium;font-family: Calibri;\"><em>Yateguwe na NIYIGABA Etienne (eniyigaba@yeanrwanda.org)</em></span></p>\r\n",
