        "id": 4287,
        "title": "Intambwe icumi (10) watera nkâ€™umuntu ushaka kwinjira mu bworozi bw'inzuki",
        "slug": null,
        "image": "inzuki.jpeg",
        "text": "<p><strong><span style=\"color:#222222\">Intambwe icumi (10) watera nk&rsquo;umuntu ushaka kwinjira mu bworozi bw&#39;inzuki.</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">1. Intambwe ya mbere ni ukuba m&rsquo; umuryango w&rsquo;aborozi b&rsquo;inzuki mu gace utuyemo. Kuko musangira amakuru y&rsquo;uko ubworozi bw&rsquo;inzuki buhagaze ,uko bukorwa ukanabaherekeza mu kazi kose kajyanye n&rsquo;ubworozi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">2. Niba utamenyereye gukora mu nzuki birashoboka ko wakwiga ibyerekeranye nazo hamwe nabaho basanzwe bazoroye</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">3. Nanone ushobora kurumwa n&rsquo;inzuki mbere yuko wowe ubwawe utangira ubworozi bwazo, umworozi agomba kumvikana nazo kuko uba ungomba kuba inshuti n&rsquo;inzuki.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">4. Igihe wabaye umunyamuryango w&rsquo;aborozi b&#39;inzuki bo mugace utuyemo, mukagirana umubano. ibitekerezo by&rsquo;uko borora bizagenda byiyongera. Ibibazobi bizakurikira nyuma yo kumenya uko ubworozi bukorwa:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">-ni inde tuzakorana?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">-ni ibihe bikoresho nzakoresha?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">-ni he nzagurisha ibikomoka ku nzuki?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">5. Niba utangiye umushinga w&#39;inzuki ugomba kwishimira gukorana n&rsquo;umuntu umwe cyangwa babiri&nbsp; muri ako gace ugiye kororeramo, uhitemo aborozi babifitiye ubushobozi (ubumenyi) kandi bumvikana. Aho nawe ingufu zawe ziziyongera. Korora inzuki ubwawe no kwifashisha uburyo butandukanye n&rsquo;uburi aho utuye n&#39;intambwe zizaguteza imbere.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">6. Nibura tangirana ubwa mbere n&rsquo;imizinga ibiri gusa. Ibi bizaguha icyigereranyo cy&rsquo;uko wakongera imizinga bitewe n&rsquo;imbaraga washyize muri yayindi ibiri bigutere imbaraga n&rsquo;ishyaka bitewe n&#39;inyungu wavanye muri ya yindi ibiri watangiranye.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">7. Mugutegura shyiraho intego z&#39;ukuri.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">Icyitonderwa: Umushinga muto ugerwaho kuko umushinga muto biroroha kuwusobanura no kuwushyira mu bikorwa kuruta umushinga munini.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">8. Ugutsinda kw&rsquo;igitekerezo no kwemerwa mu ruhando rw&rsquo;abandi borozi bishobora guterwa n&rsquo;uburyo usobanura umushingwa wawe. IGa gusobanura ibyo ukora ku rugero ruhagije.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">9. Ibikoresho ukoresha biterwa n&rsquo;imiterere yahantu uri: Ugomba guhitamo ibikoresho bitewe n&rsquo;ahantu uri, n&#39;abatekenisiye bahari, bakagufasha guhitamo ubwoko bw&#39;imizinga n&#39;ibikoresho wakoresha utangira ubworozi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#222222\">10.Kumenya abantu bakora ibikoresho byifashishwa mubworozi bw&#39;inzuki kugirango bijye biguha icyizere cy&rsquo;uwo muzajya mukorana n&rsquo;ubuzirangenge bwabyo.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><em>Icyitonderwa: Ibikubiye muri iyi nyandiko ni ibitekerezo by&rsquo;uwayanditse. Ntago bihagarariye cyangwa ari ibya YEAN</em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><em>Inyandiko yanditswe na <strong>Twahirwa Leonard&nbsp;</strong></em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:left\"><span style=\"color:#222222\"><strong><em>Twahirwa Leonard</em></strong><em> ni umuvumvu wabigize umwuga wize ubuzima bw&rsquo;amatungo (animal health) mu mashuli yisumbuye, naho muri kaminuza akurikira ibijyanye no kwita k&rsquo;urusobe rw&rsquo;ibinyabuzima (wildlife management), akaba yaranagize amahugurwa atandukanye ku bworozi bwa kinyamwuga bw&rsquo;inzuki. Akorera ubuvumvu mu turere twa Nyamagabe na Rusizi.</em></span></p>\r\n",
